    public function run()
    {
        DB::statement("SET FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS=0;");
        DB::table("user_daily_tips")->truncate();
        DB::table("daily_tips")->truncate();
        DB::statement("SET FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS=1;");


        $dailyTips = [

            // Trait seeder

            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Start Your Day with Reflection", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait provides you with an innate ability to see the big picture. Today, incorporate a period of quiet contemplation. Set aside 15–20 minutes and take a look at all of the pieces of your day (or week). Notice any potential challenges and notice the pathways to create solutions to benefit all.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Delegate Tasks", "description" => "<p>Because your Regal Trait represents the natural leader in you, today pay close attention to opportunities for delegating tasks in all areas of your life. Identify tasks that can be assigned to others and empower team or family members by providing clear instructions and support. This allows you to concentrate on your strengths while empowering others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Activate Leadership in Various Aspects", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait represents the natural leader in you. Spend time today seeing where you can activate leadership activities in various aspects of your life. Consider volunteering to lead a community project or charity event, mentoring a younger colleague or student, or overseeing a family gathering, remembering that leadership isn't confined to the workplace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Harness Your Panoramic Perspective", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait provides you with the natural ability to see the whole picture. To harness your panoramic perspective, set aside time today to find solutions to challenges in your life. Facilitate a brainstorming session with your team or family, create a mind map to visualize problems and their interconnections, or simply look at issues from multiple angles before making decisions. Use your ability to see the whole picture to develop comprehensive solutions that benefit everyone involved.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Embrace Your Benevolent Nature", "description" => "<p>Today, embrace your benevolent nature that is reflected through your Regal Trait by finding ways to contribute to the well-being of others and your community. See where you could dedicate some of your time to support others in seeing the big picture of what they may be experiencing, helping colleagues or friends find solutions, and practicing random acts of kindness throughout your day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Focus on Big-Picture Activities", "description" => "<p>Because you have a prominent Regal Trait, take time today to focus on activities that allow you to take a big-picture approach. Envision all the pieces of your day — your personal goals, family objectives, and any work or community projects in which you are involved. Utilize your ability to see all components of a situation as a valuable asset in any planning process.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Clarify Your Pondering Nature", "description" => "<p>Because you have a prominent Regal Trait, you see all the pieces and there will often be a pause while you take things in. Be aware today (and every day) that others can misinterpret your pondering nature. If you notice people perceiving you as aloof or indecisive, take a moment to explain that you're considering all pieces of the puzzle to see where they fit in the bigger picture; this can prevent misunderstandings with others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Practice Active Listening", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait makes you a natural diplomat. Today, practice active listening in all your interactions by giving your full attention to others, acknowledging their perspectives, and demonstrating that you value their input, reinforcing your diplomatic nature and helping prevent misunderstandings.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Apply Solutions Benefiting the Whole", "description" => "<p>Recognize your natural ability to see solutions that benefit the whole is reflected through your Regal Trait. When faced with any challenges today, consciously apply your panoramic perspective by considering how your solution might affect all involved parties. Propose ideas that create win-win situations, and share your solutions by highlighting benefits for everyone concerned.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Promptly Address Issues", "description" => "<p>Because your Regal Trait commands respect by its very nature, you will be impacted when disrespect is present. It's important today (and every day) to communicate your expectations clearly and respectfully, addressing any perceived disrespect promptly and diplomatically, and recognizing and appreciating when others show you respect.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Delegate Effectively", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait reveals the natural leader in you and it's also where delegation lives. To optimize your day today, focus on delegating tasks effectively by identifying specific tasks that can be delegated to others. Empower team members or family members by assigning them responsibilities, and provide clear instructions and support for the delegated tasks. This will open the time and space for you to concentrate on developing high-level solutions.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Maintain Natural Authority", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait commands respect by its very nature. Be aware of how you present yourself and interact with others to maintain your natural authority. Today, practice maintaining a confident and open posture, speak clearly and thoughtfully with moments of reflection, and cultivate a genuine interest in others' perspectives and ideas.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Balance Leadership with Listening", "description" => "<p>To embody your best self today, balance your natural leadership responsibilities, revealed through your Regal Trait, with moments of actively listening to others. Take time to listen to others today without immediately offering solutions. Show appreciation for the efforts and contributions of those around you and practice patience when others need time to process information or make decisions.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Make a Positive Impact", "description" => "<p>Today, recognize that your Regal Trait provides you with the innate ability to see solutions that benefit the greater good. Use this ability to make a positive impact today (and every day) as you see how solutions affect all parties. Propose win-win ideas and share your solutions by highlighting benefits for everyone.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Seek Leadership Opportunities", "description" => "<p>Your Regal Trait makes you a natural-born leader. Explore opportunities today to lead and guide others in various aspects of life — like volunteering for a community project or charity event, offering to mentor a younger colleague or student, or overseeing a family gathering.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Practice Presence", "description" => "<p>Because your Regal Trait provides you with the natural ability to see life from a whole picture perspective, this can sometimes take you out of the present and into the future as you observe all the pieces at hand. Throughout the day today, practice being fully present in each moment by noticing the details of the moment. Whether you're in a meeting, having a conversation, or engaging in personal activities, pay special attention to observing the details of what you are experiencing. This helps you remain present and respond effectively to others and situations.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SA", "title" => "Discovering Solutions to Benefit the Whole", "description" => "<p>Engage in activities today that activate your Regal Trait. This part of your nature sees all the pieces of a situation and finds solutions that benefit the whole. Activities like brainstorming sessions, visualizing solutions and their interconnections, and practicing looking at issues from multiple angles are all excellent ways to engage this strength.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Channel Your Energy Productively", "description" => "<p>Today, engage your Energetic Trait by channeling your passion into productive activities that help you to get things done, allowing your natural enthusiasm to initiate momentum.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Cultivate Patience", "description" => "<p>Because your Energetic Trait naturally tends to react in a more direct manner, today (and every day), practice patience by counting to ten when feeling frustrated, allowing yourself a moment to breathe before reacting. This strategy can temper any abruptness and improve interactions with others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Manage Your Direct Approach", "description" => "<p>Your more direct approach in life is reflected through your Energetic Trait. It's an asset in your life as it allows you to tackle things head-on. Just remember, at times, others may misunderstand the abrupt manner in which you respond or interact. Today, pay attention to how your actions and words affect those around you and communicate your natural tendency to take a direct route.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Temper Your Natural Intensity", "description" => "<p>Your Energetic Trait has a directness that can be both a strength and a potential source of misunderstanding for others. Today (and every day), consider tempering your natural intensity by following these practices:</p><ol><li>Count to ten when feeling frustrated and before reacting</li><li>Practice deep breathing exercises throughout the day</li><li>Practice active listening in conversations</li></ol>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Embrace Your Warrior Spirit", "description" => "<p>The innate tendency of your Energetic Trait is to “right the wrong” in a situation. When confronting challenges today (or any day), remember to temper your input with diplomacy. Your courage in facing issues head-on is admirable, but a tactful approach can lead to better outcomes. Here are some suggestions:</p><ol><li>Before addressing an issue, write down your thoughts</li><li>Ask for input before making major decisions</li><li>Seek a mediator for potentially contentious discussions</li></ol>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Maximize Your Energetic Trait", "description" => "<p>Your Energetic Trait makes you naturally productive, and effective time management can make your day efficient. Implement a time-blocking technique today to remain energy efficient around the work you want to get done (e.g. work for 90-minute time blocks, then take a 15-minute break, or work for 40 minutes, then take a 5-minute break). Structuring your day this way can help you maximize your energy output throughout the day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Your Words Carry Weight", "description" => "<p>Pay close attention to the power of your words today. Because your Energetic Trait can be direct and even abrupt when it responds at times, practice adjusting your responses today to be in alignment with your innate desire to honor others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Let Your Integrity Be Your Guide", "description" => "<p>Your commitment to truth and justice is an integral part of you as it lives in your Energetic Trait, and it can set a powerful example for those around you. Take a moment today and remember the last time you stood up for what’s right and how you handled it. As you move forward in life, remind yourself to always let your integrity lead the way in making choices rather than allowing any anger that might be sparked from a situation lead the way.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Explain Your Directness", "description" => "<p>Because your Energetic Trait is straightforward, today, explain this direct aspect of your nature to another. It can help them understand you better and eliminate misunderstandings around any abruptness they may feel coming from you at times.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Add a Friendly Comment", "description" => "<p>Your Energetic Trait gets straight to the point. Today, practice adding a friendly comment before discussing business.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "The Optimal Way to “Fix”", "description" => "<p>Your Energetic Trait makes you good at fixing problems—and it makes you naturally more direct. Today, practice softening your directness with certain individuals in an effort to activate the most efficient pathways to solve the problem and avoid upsetting others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MA", "title" => "Managing the “Crisis”", "description" => "<p>Your Energetic Trait provides you with an innate ability to manage a crisis. If a problem comes up today (or any day), remember to take a deep breath and tackle it head-on.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Connect with Others", "description" => "<p>Schedule time today to connect with a family member, friend, or colleague who might benefit from your support. Your Absorptive Trait is naturally empathetic and provides reassurance and strength for others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Discover a Solution", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait makes you a natural solutionist and your ability to access common-sense wisdom can make a significant impact on those around you. Today, put focus on discovering a solution to something that's not working, whether it be at home, in your community, or in your workplace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Dedicate Time to Learning", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait has you drawn to knowledge. Today, set aside dedicated time to learn something new, feeding your natural curiosity and expanding your vast knowledge base, which you can effortlessly draw upon in the future.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Spread Joy", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait naturally provides you with a cheerful disposition. Spread joy today by sharing a positive story or compliment with at least three people, brightening their day and reinforcing your engaging nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Initiate Collaboration", "description" => "<p>Because your Absorptive Trait makes you naturally collaborative, initiate a group activity or discussion at work or in your social circle today. Engaging this gregarious, collaborative aspect of your nature can foster team spirit and connectedness.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Practice Letting Go", "description" => "<p>Because your Absorptive Trait has a natural tendency to attach (or hold on) to things in your life a bit longer, design a 'let go' practice today by identifying one small resentment or worry and consciously release it. Get creative...you may choose to picture releasing it into the wind, into a bubble that floats away or perhaps into a river or stream. This type of daily practice promotes greater harmony within as you release thoughts that no longer serve you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Share Your Generosity", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait makes you naturally generous. Today, make a conscious choice to share with others…whether it’s offering advice, resources, or simply giving your time to someone in need, embodying your natural generosity.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Frame Your Insights Thoughtfully", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait gives you natural access to vast amounts of archived wisdom. When sharing with others today, practice framing your wisdom as personal experiences rather than absolute truths by using phrases like 'In my experience...' to make your insights more relatable.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Ask Thoughtful Questions", "description" => "<p>Because you have a prominent Absorptive Trait, this provides you with an innate desire to help others. To support others in the most optimal way, channel your desire to help today by asking thoughtful questions, allowing others to discover solutions themselves while still benefiting from your valuable wisdom.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Encourage Shared Learning", "description" => "<p>Because your Absorptive Trait allows you to archive vast amounts of knowledge, you often have the answers. When engaging with others today, instead of providing the answer, suggest looking up information together, fostering a shared learning experience and nurturing your collaborative spirit.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Gauge Appropriateness", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait makes you naturally empathetic and this can cause you to want to help alleviate another’s pain or challenge. Take a moment before responding to someone today who is experiencing a challenge and consider if it's appropriate to share your knowledge with them or if it's better to hold back. This awareness will ensure your contributions are well-received. Remember, just your presence in another’s life is so often more than enough.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Create Open Dialogue", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait, by its very nature, is engaging…and you have a lot of knowledge to share. Today, create an open dialogue with another where sharing your knowledge feels like a mutual exchange. This helps strengthen your connections and eliminates the impression of lecturing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Prioritize Your Well-being", "description" => "<p>Remember that your Absorptive Trait is where empathy lives. Because you are empathetic by nature, it’s important to recognize that 'being there' for others requires stability; today, prioritize your own well-being before deeply engaging with another’s pain or challenge. This will ensure you're grounded and present when offering support.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Engage in Storytelling", "description" => "<p>Your prominent Absorptive Trait contributes to you being a natural at storytelling. Today, share a personal story with another that imparts wisdom or joy. This is an effective way to connect with others and share your valuable insights.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Celebrate Your Joyful Nature", "description" => "<p>Throughout the day, embrace and share your joyful disposition that is reflected through your Absorptive Trait by engaging in activities that make you happy and spreading positivity to those around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Offer a Helping Hand", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait makes you naturally generous and helpful. Today, look for opportunities to offer assistance to someone in need. And when you help another, recognize the shift that occurs for them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Practice Becoming Aware of How You Eat", "description" => "<p>Because your Absorptive Trait, by its very nature, absorbs and 'holds onto'... this can have an impact on your physical body. Pay special attention today and honor your body's needs by choosing nourishing foods that support your well-being and reflect your natural harmony with life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Share Your Knowledge", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait naturally stores within you a vast 'library of understanding.' Today, help someone discover a solution to a challenge by offering your insights in your uniquely supportive and collaborative way.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "JO", "title" => "Collaborate on a Project", "description" => "<p>Your Absorptive Trait naturally draws you to collaborative approaches. Today, collaborate with others on a project or idea, or set a future collaborative dynamic in motion. Pay attention to how this shared experience and collective wisdom that comes from teamwork creates value for everyone involved.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Set Aside Alone Time", "description" => "<p>Because your Romantic Trait is more reclusive by nature, set aside dedicated \"alone time\" today to connect with this solitary aspect within you. Create a cozy, private space where you can retreat without interruptions, ensuring you have regular opportunities to recharge today and in the future.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Personalize Your Surroundings", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait has you naturally desiring an intimate rapport with your surroundings. Today, personalize your workspace…consider the objects you have in your space and make sure they are meaningful, consider the lighting, and any other factors that allow you to create a comfortable environment that resonates with this more reclusive aspect of your nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Connect with Water", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait has you naturally drawn to water. Experiencing its flow is harmonizing for you. If possible, spend time near a live body of water today—whether it's the ocean, a lake, or a stream. If this isn’t feasible, listen to recordings of water sounds or consider adding a small fountain to your space to incorporate the element of water into your daily routine.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Communicate Your Need for Focus", "description" => "<p>The more reclusive side to your nature is reflected in your Romantic Trait. This part of you works best on your own with no interruptions. Today, communicate your need for uninterrupted work time to colleagues or family members. Consider incorporating \"do not disturb\" signs or signals to indicate when you're in deep focus mode, allowing you to be more productive.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Practice Assertiveness", "description" => "<p>The more non-confrontational aspect of your nature is revealed through your Romantic Trait. It’s important to pay attention to this part of your nature so you don’t end up sacrificing your wants and needs. Today, practice expressing your needs and boundaries in a gentle but clear manner, ensuring your voice is heard without causing discomfort.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Cultivate Thankfulness", "description" => "<p>Because your Romantic Trait can be nostalgic at times, this can lead to melancholy thoughts and feelings. This is normal and natural for you but it’s also important to not let the melancholy gain too much traction in your life and keep you in a sad state for too long. Take a few minutes today and write down three things for which you are thankful. Continue to add to this list, and revisit it whenever you need a gentle reminder of the good, supportive aspects in your life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Create a Daily Ritual", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait has you thriving in quiet and secure environments. Spend a few minutes today and create a daily ritual that allows you to immerse yourself in serenity. You might dim the lights, play soft music, or engage in calming activities to nurture your inner peace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Engage in Solo Creativity", "description" => "<p>Because your Romantic Trait thrives in solitude, dedicate time today to a solo creative project. Whether it's writing, painting, or crafting, allow yourself to explore your artistic side free from outside expectations or distractions.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Schedule Solitude", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait requires regular retreat to stay harmonized. Create intentional alone time today by scheduling specific periods for solitude—treat these moments as essential appointments with yourself.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Avoid Confrontations", "description" => "<p>Because your Romantic Trait is inherently non-confrontational, try to avoid high-conflict situations today. Protecting your inner calm preserves the quiet serenity you naturally seek.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Opt for Low-Intensity Social Interactions", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait prefers quiet, meaningful connection over stimulation. Today, lean into one-on-one conversations or intimate gatherings that honor your need for gentler social engagement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Embrace Your Reclusive Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait includes a reclusive side that recharges in quiet. Embrace that need today by recognizing solitude not as withdrawal, but as a vital source of renewal and strength.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Limit Obligations", "description" => "<p>Because your Romantic Trait values space and autonomy, give yourself permission to say no to non-essential obligations today. Protect your energy by honoring your need for stillness and simplicity.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Limit Exposure to Crowded Spaces", "description" => "<p>The Romantic Trait in you can have you feeling overwhelmed in chaotic environments. Plan your day to avoid crowded or noisy places, and instead seek out quiet, comfortable settings that restore your inner balance.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LU", "title" => "Enjoy Silence", "description" => "<p>Your Romantic Trait is deeply nourished by silence. Throughout the day, welcome quiet moments as opportunities to reconnect with yourself and recharge those inner peaceful reserves.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Ease Into Your Day", "description" => "<p>Because you have a prominent Sympathetic Trait, this aspect in you is relaxed, laid-back and benefits from a slower start. Today, allow yourself extra time to ease into your day (or activities) without pressure or rushing. Starting calmly helps you maintain balance and presence.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Schedule a Power Nap", "description" => "<p>Your Sympathetic Trait thrives with daily restoration. Schedule a 20–30 minute nap between 2 and 5 PM today to support your natural rhythm and recharge your energy. Pay attention to how refreshed you feel—this type of midday rest is uniquely effective for you, even if it’s not for everyone.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Acknowledge Procrastination Positively", "description" => "<p>Your Sympathetic Trait often leans toward a relaxed approach to action, which can sometimes turn into procrastination. Today, reframe that tendency as a chance to notice what feels truly useful in the moment. Rather than adding pressure, let your calm pace guide you toward what matters.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Set Gentle Reminders", "description" => "<p>Because your Sympathetic Trait prefers ease over urgency, use gentle reminders today—like calendar notifications or soft alarms—to help manage your schedule. These supportive cues help you stay on track without disrupting your natural flow.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Be the Calm in the Storm", "description" => "<p>Your Sympathetic Trait allows you to maintain peace and warmth, even when others feel overwhelmed. Today, notice where you can be the “calm in the storm” for those around you. Your easygoing and charming nature naturally helps diffuse tension.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Engage in Healing Activities", "description" => "<p>The Sympathetic Trait makes you a natural-born healer—often just your presence is enough to bring comfort. Today, engage in healing activities, whether it’s listening to someone share a struggle or supporting a friend in need. If you work in the healing arts, notice how your calming energy enhances the experience for others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Reflect on Your Positive Impact", "description" => "<p>Your Sympathetic Trait has a calm, nurturing influence that uplifts those around you. This evening, take a moment to reflect on how your relaxed, warm presence positively impacts others—and how your steady nature brings others ease and reassurance.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Embrace Your Nurturing Nature", "description" => "<p>Because your Sympathetic Trait makes you a natural nurturer, today reach out to a loved one or coworker with a kind word or offer of support. These small gestures align with your nature and often make a big difference.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Optimize Your Relationship With Time", "description" => "<p>Your prominent Sympathetic Trait can bring a more fluid sense of time, which sometimes means punctuality isn’t your top priority. Today, communicate your pace clearly with others so expectations stay realistic and respectful of your rhythm.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VEN", "title" => "Transition Without Stress", "description" => "<p>Your Sympathetic Trait functions best without abrupt transitions. Allow yourself extra time this morning to ease into your day, and give yourself space between tasks to move calmly and without stress. This helps protect your energy and sustain your natural pace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Practice Active Listening", "description" => "<p>Because your Perceptive Trait processes information so quickly, it’s easy to jump ahead in conversation. Today, practice active listening by fully tuning in to others’ words before responding. This intentional awareness strengthens your connections and deepens your understanding.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Strategize Your Tasks", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait provides you with an innate ability to excel at analysis and strategy. Use this ability today to outline your most important tasks and allocate focused time for each. This will help you focus your energy efficiently toward what truly matters.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Offer Problem-Solving Support", "description" => "<p>Because your Perceptive Trait naturally spots the root of problems quickly, offer your insight today to help others navigate challenges. Your ability to clarify issues and solve problems can provide deep value for others and this can contribute to strengthening your relationship with them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Engage in Mind-Challenging Activities", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait thrives when challenging your mind. Engage in something strategically enriching today—like a puzzle, game, or challenge—to sharpen your analytical edge and activate this aspect of your nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Set Boundaries on Information Sharing", "description" => "<p>Because your Perceptive Trait is more covert by nature, you will often lean toward discretion. Today, reflect on what information you tend to withhold and consider whether sharing more could enhance trust. Being selectively transparent can still honor your need for privacy while building rapport.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Practice Transparency", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait can sometimes default to withholding information until you’re ready to share. Practice sharing more openly when appropriate today. Transparent communication fosters trust, prevents misunderstandings, and invites mutual respect.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Satisfy Your Curiosity", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait makes you naturally curious, dedicate time today to explore a new topic…this will satisfy your curiosity and keep your mind engaged.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Schedule Uninterrupted Work Time", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait provides you with the natural ability to maintain a high level of concentration. Today (and moving forward), schedule daily uninterrupted time blocks for deep work. Use this time to tackle complex problems requiring your full attention.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Help Others with Troubleshooting", "description" => "<p>As someone with a prominent Perceptive Trait, you naturally troubleshoot with ease. Use this natural ability today to help someone unravel a problem—it not only highlights your value but strengthens your relational bonds.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Review Your Work for Details", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait makes you naturally detail-oriented. Before finalizing anything today, take a few extra minutes to scan your work. Your precision can catch any overlooked details, enhancing the quality of your output.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Reflect on Territorial Tendencies", "description" => "<p>Your Perceptive Trait can cause you to experience territorial feelings at times. Today, reflect on times in the past when you’ve had possessive feelings or interactions around certain people, places and things in your life. Set an intention to practice being open to allowing experiences to unfold naturally, without needing a certain outcome. The freedom that exists in this space cultivates trust and openness.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Manage Impatience", "description" => "<p>With your Perceptive Trait’s quick processing comes the challenge of impatience. Today, give others space to express themselves fully—even if you already know “where they’re going”. Patience builds connection and fosters better communication.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MER", "title" => "Communicate Constructively", "description" => "<p>Because your Perceptive Trait makes you a natural critical thinker, remind yourself that others can, at times, receive your feedback as criticism. Today, focus on communicating your perceptions constructively, framing them in a way that is helpful and encouraging.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Engage in Creative Exploration", "description" => "<p>Your Effervescent Trait provides you with the ability to access possibility-filled solutions. Today, create the opportunity to engage with others in brainstorming sessions to explore creative solutions to anything that needs resolving.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Explore an Interest that Excites You", "description" => "<p>Since the childlike wonder that exists in your Effervescent Trait is prominent in you, dedicate time today to explore a new hobby or interest that excites you, fueling your curiosity and fun-loving nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Spread Kindness with a Smile", "description" => "<p>Your Effervescent Trait provides you with a naturally delightful disposition. Remember to smile and greet everyone you meet today, spreading kindness and uplifting the spirits of those around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Enhance Focus with Time Blocks", "description" => "<p>Your Effervescent Trait contributes to those times in your day when you are more distracted. To maintain productivity today, use a timer when you want to get work done; create an intention to focus on one thing at a time and in focused intervals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Capture Your Thoughts", "description" => "<p>Because your Effervescent Trait has such a highly refined way of processing information, information can escape you more quickly. Today, remember to capture your thoughts (or To Do’s) on paper or using digital tools or apps.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Incorporate Playfulness into Your Day", "description" => "<p>Your Effervescent Trait makes you naturally more playful. Today, remember to take breaks and engage in activities like playing games or other light-hearted activities that allow you to access this Effervescent part of your nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Communicate Fleeting Thoughts Respectfully", "description" => "<p>Your Effervescent Trait has a shorter attention span. Because of this, at times you may find yourself announcing fleeting thoughts. Today, in order to practice being more sensitive to others and your environment, when you find yourself interrupting the moment, explain to others that you are simply saying something so you can capture it and not forget it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Make Time for Fun", "description" => "<p>Having fun and making fun is a natural part of your Effervescent Trait. Ensure you find time today to 'play' in ways that inspire you, keeping your spirits high and creativity flowing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Be Mindful of Others' Perspectives", "description" => "<p>Because the Effervescent Trait in you is so fun-loving, when you are in the midst of having fun and making fun, others can sometimes not take you as seriously. Today, consider this as you engage with others. Practice recognizing that not everyone is naturally as fun-loving as you. Remind yourself not to stop the fun but rather adjust to others and the moment… without dimming your brilliant nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Set Aside Time for Reflection", "description" => "<p>Because your Effervescent Trait processes information so quickly, today, when new information comes in, set aside time for reflection to ensure you fully understand and retain the new information.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SO", "title" => "Embrace Your Childlike Wonder", "description" => "<p>Today, allow the childlike wonder that is reflected through your Effervescent Trait to lead you by playing with a child or pet, trying something new, or simply marveling at the world around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],


            // Driver seeder

            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Embrace Transformative Projects", "description" => "<p>Because your Initiating Change Driver thrives on transformation, today, identify an area in your home or workspace that feels outdated or inefficient. Begin planning how you can reimagine and improve it to better suit your evolving needs.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Seek Out Opportunities for Change", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver is naturally activated when spotting possibilities for improvement. Today, actively seek areas in your personal life, community, or workplace where you can be the catalyst for effective transformation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Reflect on Past Transformations", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver is all about transformation and it is strengthened by experience. Today, reflect on past changes you've initiated—what worked, what didn’t, and what you learned. Use these insights to shape future transformative efforts.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Engage in Discussions About Change", "description" => "<p>Because your Initiating Change Driver is constantly on a mission to make changes, seek out conversations today that explore new ideas. Share your perspectives and inspire others to embrace change through your experiences and suggestions.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Start a Small Improvement Project", "description" => "<p>Even small actions fuel your Initiating Change Driver. Select a simple activity today—like moving a small piece of furniture to a new location, refreshing a digital folder or putting a new background on one of your device screens—this allows you to engage your need to transform in small ways that keep you energized.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Support Others in Transformation", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver not only transforms your world but it can also benefit others. Identify someone who is seeking a change in their world and offer your support today, becoming a catalyst for their evolution.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Channel Frustration into Action", "description" => "<p>When frustration arises, your Initiating Change Driver seeks an outlet. To avoid escalating your frustration, remind yourself today to redirect any restless energy you may have now (and in the future) into productive change. Start a new project or make meaningful adjustments to your environment or routines.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Recognize Stagnation and Act", "description" => "<p>Stagnation is a trigger for your Initiating Change Driver. Today, (or any day), whenever the day feels still or uninspired, notice this cue and take steps—big or small—to initiate change in areas that need revitalization.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Rearrange Your Space", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver finds energy in reimagining environments. Refresh your home or office today by rearranging furniture or decor to create a new perspective and satisfy your natural desire for transformation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Plan a Big Project", "description" => "<p>Because your Initiating Change Driver is motivated by bold transformation, start planning a significant project today—such as renovating a room or launching a personal challenge. This will engage your deeper desire for meaningful change.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Adopt a New Technology", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver is sparked by innovation. Explore and adopt a new technology or tool today that can improve efficiency, helping you stay aligned with your drive for continual improvement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Improve a Process", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver is naturally drawn to inefficiencies. Identify a process at home or work today that could be better and create a plan to enhance it, making life easier for yourself and others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Embrace a Healthy Habit", "description" => "<p>Because your Initiating Change Driver craves ongoing improvement, introduce a new healthy habit today—like increasing water intake or committing to daily walks. Small consistent changes lead to meaningful transformation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DE", "title" => "Initiate a Workplace Improvement", "description" => "<p>Your Initiating Change Driver thrives in environments where change uplifts others. Propose an improvement at work or home today that enhances productivity or morale. Initiating this transformative shift energizes you and supports collective growth.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Organize Your Tasks", "description" => "<p>Because your Creating Order Driver thrives on structure, identify the top three tasks for the day and write them down. Allocate specific time slots for each task in your calendar, and review the list at the end of the day to carry over unfinished tasks.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Simplify Your Routines", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver provides you with the ability to streamline processes. Today, simplify your daily routines to save time by noting any time-wasting activities and eliminating unnecessary steps.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Tidy Up Small Areas Daily", "description" => "<p>Because you have a natural drive to Create Order, dedicate at least 10 minutes today (and every day) to tidy up a small area like a desk or a drawer, maintaining a clutter-free environment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Establish a Weekly Meal Plan", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver provides you with the natural ability to excel at creating systems. Establish a weekly meal plan today to reduce daily decision-making stress. Make a shopping list and set an intention to prepare ingredients in advance to save time during the week.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Organize Storage Spaces", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver provides you with the natural talent to maximize resources. Today, create a plan to organize your storage spaces. Schedule a decluttering session for yourself with the intention to arrange items for easy access.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Implement Time-Blocking", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver naturally helps you manage time well. Create a time-blocking system today to allocate specific times for specific tasks, enhancing focus and productivity.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Practice Transparency", "description" => "<p>When your Creating Order Driver isn’t able to create order, this can lead to manipulation. Today, practice transparency by openly sharing with others your need to create order and your specific plans and intentions. This builds trust and reduces misunderstandings.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Avoid Manipulation", "description" => "<p>Because you have Creating Order as one of your driving forces, recognize that not everyone creates order in the same way you do. Today, remind yourself to avoid using manipulation to get others to align with your orderly needs. Instead, cultivate open communication and appreciate different perspectives.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Delegate Effectively", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver helps you effectively delegate. Today, list tasks that can be delegated at work or home; identify capable individuals. When you delegate, communicate your expectations related to the task clearly, and schedule a follow up to ensure completion.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Organize Digital Files", "description" => "<p>Because you have Creating Order driving you, you are naturally skilled at arranging. Carve out time today to begin organizing your digital files and emails. Create folders and subfolders, and set an intention to regularly delete unnecessary files to keep your digital space tidy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Create Checklists for Organization", "description" => "<p>Because you have Creating Order as one of your motivating forces, use checklists today to keep track of tasks and ensure nothing is overlooked. When you create your checklists, consider prioritizing and categorizing your lists.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Use a Planning System", "description" => "<p>Because you have a Creating Order Driver… purchase, create, activate, or refine a planning system today. Whether it's a hardcover planner, a notebook or a digital App. Utilize this to schedule your tasks and appointments, maintaining order in your daily activities.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Develop Standard Procedures", "description" => "<p>Because you have Creating Order driving you, create standard operating procedure for routine tasks today. This will help you streamline processes making them more efficient.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Organize Emails", "description" => "<p>Because your Creating Order Driver needs to organize, today, begin the process of sorting your emails into folders or labels. Consider unsubscribing from unnecessary newsletters or subscriptions, and maintain an organized inbox.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Establish Routines", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Order Driver naturally aligns with routines. Today, consider what area of your life can benefit from a routine and establish a new one…perhaps it’s a self-care routine, a new eating plan, or exercise program. Remember, routines bring consistency and order to your life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Create a Daily Schedule", "description" => "<p>Because you have a Creating Order Driver, if you don’t already have a detailed schedule for your day, today allocate time for work, breaks, and personal activities. If you already have a detailed schedule for yourself, take another look at it and see where you can heighten your efficiency to stay organized and optimized.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "DOM", "title" => "Simplify Your Commitments", "description" => "<p>Review your commitments today and consider simplifying or eliminating those that no longer serve you. Your Creating Order driver will thrive as you free up time and energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Prepare a First Aid Kit", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Protection Driver provides you with the natural ability to recognize how to be prepared in many aspects of life. Today, ensure you have a well-stocked first aid kit and general emergency supplies at home and in your car. Place the kits in visible and accessible locations and set reminders to check them regularly.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Update Emergency Contacts", "description" => "<p>Spend time today updating your emergency contact list. Set an intention to review and update it every six months, share it with family members and trusted friends, and store it both digitally and in a physical address book. This practice will “feed” your Creating Protection Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Develop a Safety Plan", "description" => "<p>Your Creating Protection Driver aligns with safety. Today, begin to develop a comprehensive safety plan for your home and family, including emergency contacts, evacuation routes, and safety protocols. Schedule regular reviews and updates to keep the plan effective.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Foster Open Communication", "description" => "<p>Because you have a Creating Protection Driver, today, begin to share your understanding of your need to address safety concerns with a family member, a friend, or colleague. Explain that taking preventative measures is important to you; share that too much uncertainty around issues can even cause anxiety for you. Encourage open dialogue without labeling or judgment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Limit Exposure to Negative News", "description" => "<p>To maintain the strong state of your Creating Protection Driver, if you do feel inclined to check the news, limit your exposure and designate specific times to do so (not first thing in the morning or just before you go to sleep). Choose reliable news sources, balance news intake with positive content, and discuss concerns that may come up with trusted individuals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Utilize Safety Technology", "description" => "<p>Leverage technology for peace of mind, as you “feed” your Creating Protection Driver. Today, consider installing safety Apps, using smart home devices, and keeping software updated. Remind yourself to regularly update passwords and enable two-factor authentication to protect personal information. Any or all of these actions will Create Protection for you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Prioritize Self-Care and Relaxation", "description" => "<p>To stay in the strong state of your Creating Protection Driver, ensure you're getting enough sleep, eating well, and staying hydrated. Today, set aside time for yourself to engage in activities that align with your interests and practice relaxation techniques.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Perform Essential Safety Actions", "description" => "<p>Because you have Creating Protection as one of your drivers, today, choose at least one of the following actions to enhance safety:</p><ul><li>Check tire pressure and oil levels on your car.</li><li>Give a spare set of keys to a trusted person.</li><li>Check expiration dates on medications and restock as needed.</li><li>Place spare phone chargers in your car, office, and home.</li><li>Store flashlights in multiple locations around your home.</li><li>Program emergency contacts into your phone's speed dial.</li><li>Post a list of emergency numbers near landlines.</li><li>Designate a safe space in your home for relaxation and security.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Gather Information to Ease Anxiety", "description" => "<p>The weak state of your Creating Protection Driver can spark anxiousness in you, and if not addressed, this can escalate into feelings of panic. If you're feeling anxious today (or any day), spend time aligning with resources that support your ability to create protection. Whatever you are anxious about, seek information from reputable sources to ensure you have all the information, talk to a trusted family member, friend or colleague and share your feelings, only consume content that provides clarity and relief.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Stay Hydrated and Nourished", "description" => "<p>Today, support your Creating Protection Driver by maintaining good hydration and nutrition to keep your body functioning optimally, enhancing your resilience.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "FE", "title" => "Establish a Daily Safety Check", "description" => "<p>Because you have the Creating Protection Driver, today, set an intention to inspect your home or workspace for potential hazards. Set a specific time each day, (or each month or year), and make a short checklist of items to review (like locks, oven or stoves left on, smoke detectors, electrical outlets, carbon monoxide detectors), and address any issues promptly.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Review Your Budget Weekly", "description" => "<p>Because you have Monetary Discernment driving you, if you don’t already have this in place, today, set a weekly reminder to review your budget. This will allow you to track your income and expenses to ensure a harmonious flow of money.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Allocate Time for Financial Planning", "description" => "<p>Set aside time today (and several times a week) for financial planning. This practice will fuel your Monetary Discernment Driver and keep you optimized.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Engage in Charitable Giving", "description" => "<p>Today, explore where you might begin a practice of consistent tithing or charitable giving. This activity fuels the strong state of your Monetary Discernment Driver by enhancing your sense of contribution and keeping you in a harmonious flow with money.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Monitor Your Credit Score Monthly", "description" => "<p>Today, calendar a date every month to monitor your credit score. Keeping an eye on your credit will help you maintain financial health and fuel your Monetary Discernment Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Optimize the Flow of Money", "description" => "<p>Today, consider where you can optimize the harmonious flow of money in your life. Use budgeting apps to create an optimal budget and track your daily expenses. This will ensure you stay in the strong state of your Monetary Discernment Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Declutter and Purge Excess Items", "description" => "<p>With Monetary Discernment driving you, remember, maintaining harmonious flow isn't just about money; it also relates to possessions. Today, consider decluttering your space by purging items you no longer need, restoring harmony to your space.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Reinvest Profits for Growth", "description" => "<p>Your Monetary Discernment Driver understands that it takes money to make money. Today, consider where you can reinvest your profits into growth opportunities to enhance your financial position.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Explore Passive Income Opportunities", "description" => "<p>Seek opportunities for passive income to enhance your financial portfolio. Today, set aside some time to research options like real estate, dividends, or other investments. These opportunities (and others) “feed” the strong state of your Monetary Discernment Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Automate Your Savings", "description" => "<p>Today, if you’re not already doing so, consider automating your savings to ensure consistent contributions to your emergency fund, retirement accounts, and investment portfolios. This is a great way to “feed” the strong state of your Monetary Discernment Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Recognize Signs of Gluttony", "description" => "<p>Be mindful of the weak state of your Monetary Discernment Driver, which is gluttony. Today, reflect on areas where you may be overindulging and take steps to restore harmony.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "GRE", "title" => "Review Subscriptions and Memberships", "description" => "<p>Today, take some time and evaluate recurring expenses like subscriptions and memberships. Make a choice to cancel those that no longer provide value to optimize your spending. This strategy “feeds” the strong state of your Monetary Discernment Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Embrace Your Natural Impulses", "description" => "<p>Because you have Spontaneity as one of your drivers, allow yourself to act on a sudden idea today without overthinking it. This could lead to a new creative breakthrough.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Start an Idea Journal", "description" => "<p>Your Spontaneity Driver provides you with endless, outside-the-box ideas. Today, start an idea journal. Keep it handy to capture your thoughts whenever an idea “pops in.”</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Use Voice Memos", "description" => "<p>Because you have Spontaneity driving you, you experience a lot of ideas throughout each day. Today, set an intention to use voice memos to record your thoughts as they come. This will help you manage and revisit your spontaneous insights.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Dedicate Time to Creative Activities", "description" => "<p>Your Spontaneity Driver thrives on creativity. Dedicate time today to any creative activity you enjoy to keep your genius nourished.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Seek Innovative Environments", "description" => "<p>Seek out environments today that encourage innovation and idea sharing. This will help you stay in a strong state by feeding your Spontaneity Driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Raise Your Serotonin Levels", "description" => "<p>Raise your serotonin levels today by spending time in sunlight and engaging in physical activities. This will help keep you in the strong state of your Spontaneity Driver and prevent you from swinging into the high or low spaces of the weak state of this driver.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Communicate in Judgment-Free Spaces", "description" => "<p>Because you have Spontaneity driving you, there are times when you can feel misunderstood by others. Today, focus on communicating your ideas in judgment-free spaces; align with people in your life who are kind, accepting, and inclusive. This will prevent feelings of being misunderstood, which can lead to manic states.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Take Micro Moments for Unplanned Activities", "description" => "<p>Because your Spontaneity Driver thrives on variety and the freedom to act in the moment, take micro moments throughout your day to engage in unplanned activities. Whether it's a quick walk, a spontaneous conversation, or diving into a hobby, these moments fuel your natural rhythm and keep your energy flowing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Channel Energy through Expressive Arts", "description" => "<p>Your Spontaneity Driver generates bursts of creative energy that need outlets. Today, explore expressive arts—painting, drawing, music, or writing—to channel this dynamic force into tangible and fulfilling expressions, preventing overwhelm and maintaining inner harmony.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Engage in Discussions with Diverse Groups", "description" => "<p>Because your Spontaneity Driver gives you access to fresh and unconventional ideas, seek out conversations with diverse people today. Engaging in unexpected dialogues will broaden your perspective and refine your naturally visionary thoughts.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Connect with Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Spontaneity Driver can at times create a whirlwind of mental activity. To ground and harmonize this energy, spend time in nature today. Walk barefoot, rest against a tree, or simply observe your surroundings. This natural reset supports clarity and calm while still honoring your need for dynamic movement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Let Ideas Flow Freely", "description" => "<p>Your Spontaneity Driver loves unrestricted creativity. Set aside time today to brainstorm or free-write without judgment. Let your mind wander and explore—some of your best ideas will emerge when you allow space for and capture your unfiltered thought.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Embrace Last-Minute Invitations", "description" => "<p>Because your Spontaneity Driver flourishes in the unexpected, say yes to a last-minute opportunity today if it feels right. Allow yourself to break from the norm and experience the freedom that spontaneity naturally brings you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LUN", "title" => "Balance Spontaneity with Gentle Structure", "description" => "<p>While your Spontaneity Driver craves freedom, a little structure can help guide your bursts of energy productively. Today, set loose boundaries around your time so you can flow freely without feeling scattered. Block out general periods (like 'creative time,' 'email/communication window,' or 'movement break') so you have structure but freedom within it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Thankfulness", "description" => "<p>Because you have Optimism driving you, spend some time today recognizing what you are thankful for in your life. Write down three things you are thankful for today, share one with a friend or family member, and reflect on how this thankfulness exercise impacts your day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "See Opportunities in Challenges", "description" => "<p>Your Optimism Driver provides you with the ability to identify opportunities within the challenges of life. Today, identify one challenge you are facing, list three possible positive outcomes from this challenge, and take one small step towards achieving one of these outcomes.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Surround Yourself with Positivity", "description" => "<p>Because you have Optimism driving you, surrounding yourself with positivity is important. Today, spend time with people who uplift and inspire you, listen to motivational podcasts or music, or play with a child or animal.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Spread Good Cheer", "description" => "<p>Your Optimism Driver encourages you to spread good cheer. Today, perform a random act of kindness for someone, compliment a colleague or friend sincerely, or share a positive story or joke with someone.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Find Silver Linings", "description" => "<p>Because you have Optimism driving you, you can find the silver lining in most situations. As you go about your day, tune into when something not so optimal occurs. When it does, find one opportunity in what occurred and share this with someone involved in the situation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Replace Immaturity with Optimism", "description" => "<p>When you are not 'fueling' your Optimism Driver in its strong state, you will be accessing its weak state which is immature behavior. Today, pay attention to any immature thoughts or feelings you may be having. If you recognize that you've been deflated, quickly replace immaturity with an optimistic activity to restore your energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Create Fun and Excitement", "description" => "<p>Because you have Optimism driving you, create some fun and excitement in your activities today. Turn a mundane task into a game or challenge, plan a surprise for someone you care about, or add an element of fun to your work environment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Perform Random Acts of Kindness", "description" => "<p>Your Optimism Driver encourages you to participate in random acts of kindness. Today, open the door for someone, smile at someone, or leave an uplifting note for someone to find.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Foster Positive Relationships", "description" => "<p>Your Optimism Driver encourages you to create possibility-filled solutions in relationships. Today, discuss future plans and dreams with a partner or friend, work together to uncover a solution to a problem, or celebrate a shared success or milestone.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NAI", "title" => "Engage in Playful Activities", "description" => "<p>Because you have Optimism driving you, engage in playful activities today. Spend time playing with children or pets, visit a local amusement park or recreational area, or have a game night with friends or family.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Practice Active Listening", "description" => "<p>Because you have Humility driving you, you are a natural listener. Today, heighten your listening skills by practicing active listening. When you listen to someone today, reflect back what you hear to ensure understanding and ask open-ended questions to encourage deeper conversation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Recognize When to Recharge", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver needs to find the harmony between engaging with others and stepping away to recharge. Today, practice recognizing when it’s time for you to recharge. Set aside specific times for solitude and communicate your need for alone time to those around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Be a Grounding Presence", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver is naturally grounding for others. Today, offer support and reassurance to someone during a stressful time. Be the calming presence in chaotic environments and provide a listening ear without judgment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Maintain Balance to Avoid Neglect", "description" => "<p>The weak state of your Humility Driver is Neglect. Today, reflect on what the harmony between engaging with others and taking time for yourself looks like for you. Recognize signs when you've been 'on' too long with others or when you've been in recharge mode (away from others) too long, and adjust accordingly.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Educate Others About Your Needs", "description" => "<p>Because you have Humility as one of your Drivers, educate another (or others) today on your need for recharge time. Explain the importance of alone time for your well-being, set boundaries around your availability, and encourage loved ones to respect your need for solitude.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Learn to Say 'No' When Necessary", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver often impacts your ability to say 'no.' Today, pay attention to what you say 'yes' to, ensuring that you are not overextending yourself. Practice politely declining requests that overfill your plate.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Connect with Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver makes it easy for you to connect with nature. It’s reviving and rejuvenating for you. Today, spend time outdoors in a place that brings you peace. Consider exploring new natural environments and make a plan to spend consistent time in nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Be Mindful of Being Taken Advantage Of", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver provides you with a natural graciousness. This is a fine quality…and it can also lead others to take advantage of you at times. Today, be mindful of agreeing to things out of obligation rather than desire. Ensure that your commitments align with your well-being.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Balance Engagement and Solitude", "description" => "<p>To maintain harmony with your Humility Driver, balance your time today (and every day) between social interactions and solitude. Monitor your energy levels to prevent burnout and adjust your schedule to include both engagement and recharge time.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Embrace Your Talents Modestly", "description" => "<p>There is a modesty that exists in your Humility Driver. Today, rather than dismissing your talents, reflect on how they benefit others. Accept compliments from others with your natural graciousness and use your strengths to support and uplift those around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Honor Your Inner Stillness", "description" => "<p>Your Humility Driver finds strength in stillness and quiet. Set aside time today to simply sit, breathe, and be present without stimulation. This intentional pause nourishes your internal balance and allows you to reconnect with your grounded nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Break Down Big Goals", "description" => "<p>Because you have Accomplishment as one of your Drivers, consider the big goals you have for yourself. Today, spend time breaking those goals into smaller, manageable tasks that can be accomplished today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Track Your Progress", "description" => "<p>With Accomplishment as one of your Drivers, winning is important to you. Begin tracking your progress today by keeping a journal or using an app to log daily achievements and reflect on your progress.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Celebrate Small Victories", "description" => "<p>Your Accomplishment Driver motivates you to set lofty goals. Today, celebrate your small victories by acknowledging and rewarding yourself for recent achievements to maintain energy and enthusiasm.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Commit to a New Habit", "description" => "<p>Your Accomplishment Driver provides you with a strong work ethic. Today, commit to one new habit that directly supports your goal-oriented lifestyle.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Set Realistic Benchmarks", "description" => "<p>Because you have Accomplishment as a Driver, today review or refine your benchmarks related to your most important goal. Ensure that your goals are challenging yet attainable.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Schedule Goal-Setting Sessions", "description" => "<p>Your Accomplishment Driver needs goals as your 'oxygen'. Today, schedule a goal-setting session and dedicate time each week to review and adjust your goals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Respect Others' Perspectives", "description" => "<p>Remember that not everyone shares your drive for Accomplishment. Today, pay attention to others' perspectives and practice withholding any judgment or imposing your standards on them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Create a Backup Goals List", "description" => "<p>Because your Accomplishment Driver is naturally restless without objectives, begin a list of backup goals today. These are alternative goals you can pursue if you complete your primary ones early.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Seek Feedback", "description" => "<p>Your Accomplishment Driver is constantly on a mission to accomplish the big goals you have for yourself and in your life. Today, seek feedback or input from trusted peers to refine your strategies and improve outcomes. This collaboration can enhance your effectiveness.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Embrace Your Drive for Accomplishment", "description" => "<p>Today, take a moment and recognize and appreciate your innate ability to achieve that is reflected through your Accomplishment Driver. Use this as a powerful force to propel you toward your goals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Reflect on Daily Accomplishments", "description" => "<p>With Accomplishment as one of your driving forces, at the end of your day today, reflect on what you've accomplished today as you plan for the next day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POW", "title" => "Review Goals Regularly", "description" => "<p>With Accomplishment as one of your Drivers, take time today to assess your current goals to ensure they remain aligned with all that you wish to achieve.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Care for a Living Being", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver provides you with an innate desire to care for living things. Today, choose at least one activity that allows you to care for the needs of a person, plant, or animal.</p><ul><li>Do something helpful for someone.</li><li>Spend time gardening or watering houseplants.</li><li>Walk or play with a pet.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Reconnect with Others", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver seeks to be helpful to others. Today, reach out to a friend you haven't spoken to in a while, organize a small gathering to foster connections, or join a community group with shared interests.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Offer Assistance", "description" => "<p>Because your Compassion Driver thrives on helping others, offer your assistance to someone today.</p><ul><li>Help a neighbor with a task or chore.</li><li>Offer your skills or expertise to someone in need.</li><li>Be available to listen and support those around you.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Be Aware of Others' Needs", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver encourages you to be aware of others' needs. Today, anticipate the needs of those around you. Offer help before being asked and be considerate of others' feelings and circumstances.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Perform Acts of Kindness", "description" => "<p>Because you have Compassion driving you, caring for others is a primary focus. Today, engage in one or more acts of kindness, such as:</p><ul><li>Performing a random act of kindness for a stranger.</li><li>Complimenting someone genuinely.</li><li>Sending a 'thinking of you' card to someone.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Explore Ways to Serve Your Community", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver thrives on being of service to others. Today, explore ways you could serve your community:</p><ul><li>Find a local charity or organization that aligns with your values.</li><li>Dedicate a specific time each week to volunteer.</li><li>Encourage a friend to join you in volunteering.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Reflect on How You Care for Others", "description" => "<p>The weak state of your Compassion driver is 'Woe-Is-Me.' This feeling arises when you don't provide yourself with enough opportunities to care for others. Today, set aside time to write down the different ways you care for living things. Use this list as a resource to remind yourself to engage with life in compassionate ways.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Practice Self-Care", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver has you naturally caring deeply about outcomes. Because of this, disappointment can hit hard. To avoid feeling overwhelmed, it's important to practice self-care. Today (and every day):</p><ul><li>Set aside 15 minutes for relaxation.</li><li>Make healthy food choices.</li><li>Stay properly hydrated.</li><li>Ensure you get enough sleep.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Avoid Self-Sacrifice", "description" => "<p>Your Compassion Driver thrives when being of service, but there's a fine line between serving others and sacrificing yourself. Today, consider ways you may have overextended yourself in the past. Remind yourself that you can help others without sacrificing your own needs.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "SP", "title" => "Make a Difference Today", "description" => "<p>Focus on making a difference in someone else's life – it’s 'fuel' for your Compassion Driver. Do something nice and helpful for someone. Here are some suggestions:</p><ul><li>Lend a supportive ear to someone who needs to talk.</li><li>Send a loving note, text, or email to someone.</li><li>Give a thoughtful gift to someone.</li><li>Bring a meal or dessert to a friend or family member.</li></ul>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Diversify Your Day", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver thrives on variety. Switch up how you engage in your daily activities today (and every day) to keep things fresh and exciting.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Try a New Hobby", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver provides you with a love for exploration. Today, set an intention to dedicate time each week to try a new hobby or activity.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Attend Local Events", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver relishes new experiences. Today, check out an event calendar for your area. Plan to attend the next cultural event, concert, festival, or exhibition that interests you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Change Your Work Setting", "description" => "<p>To keep your professional life varied, and your Traveler Driver optimized, set an intention to change your work setting occasionally — starting today! Work from a different space within your home or office, or visit a coffee shop, café, or co-working space.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Incorporate Varied Exercise", "description" => "<p>When it comes to exercise, your Traveler Driver needs daily variety. Choose a different type of physical activity today — like walking, hiking, dancing, or any activity that provides a new experience.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Discover New Media", "description" => "<p>Because your Traveler Driver needs variety in all aspects of life, take a break today and discover new music, podcasts, or virtual experiences that align with your interests. This is one way to nourish your Traveler Driver and keep you energized.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Take a New Route", "description" => "<p>Because your Traveler Driver draws you to adventure, take a new route home from work today. If you have more time, embark on a day excursion to a nearby town or nature spot.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Experiment with Cuisine", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver loves diversity. Today, experiment with cooking a recipe from a different cuisine or visit a new restaurant.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Vary Your Entertainment", "description" => "<p>Because your Traveler Driver seeks variety in every aspect of life, consider even switching up the type of media you consume or engage in. Today, watch a different genre of movie or TV show, or explore a new podcast.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Plan a Trip", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver loves to travel! Take time today to explore your next travel destination, whether it's a big adventure or a variety-filled 'staycation.' Write down a list of places you want to visit or stay.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "TRA", "title" => "Connect with New People", "description" => "<p>Your Traveler Driver loves variety. Engage in conversations with someone new today. Networking can open doors to fresh experiences and perspectives.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Appreciate Beauty Today", "description" => "<p>Because you have Aesthetic Sensibility driving you, spend time today appreciating a piece of art, music, or something beautiful in nature. This will feed your innate need for beauty.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Dress Expressively", "description" => "<p>Because you have the Aesthetic Sensibility Driver, remember, your appreciation for beauty can be accessed in all areas of life, including your daily attire. Today, take time to dress in a way that makes you feel confident and expressive, boosting your mood and self-esteem.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Seek Opportunities to Perform", "description" => "<p>Because your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver is performance-oriented, seek opportunities today, and every day, to present your talents to the world. This could be through sports, creative arts, music, dance, speaking, or design.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Give Genuine Compliments", "description" => "<p>Your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver is energized by positive reception. Today, practice giving genuine compliments to others to foster a supportive environment where you also will naturally receive acknowledgment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Curate a Personal Collection", "description" => "<p>Because you have Aesthetic Sensibility driving you, surrounding yourself with beauty energizes and optimizes you. Today, set an intention to curate your personal collection of beauty. Notice the types of things that are beautiful to you. It could be art, books, photography, music, clothes, shoes or any other items, images or experiences that align with your eye for beauty. It’s not about the quantity - it’s about what energizes you when you look, listen or experience something.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Explore Places of Beauty", "description" => "<p>Because you have Aesthetic Sensibility driving you, you naturally have a keen eye for beauty in all aspects of life. Explore or visit a place of beauty today that inspires you, such as an art gallery, scenic park, or unique café.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Share Your Creative Talents", "description" => "<p>Your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver thrives when you share your gifts and receive feedback. Today, share your creative talents with a friend or online community and notice how the feedback makes you feel.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Be Aware of Self-Absorption", "description" => "<p>The strong state of your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver is naturally performance oriented and its weak state is Self Absorption. Pay attention today to moments when you find yourself longing for or seeking feedback, attention, or praise from others. Recognize that seeking validation indicates you are operating in the weak state of self-absorption. To get back into the strong state of your Aesthetic Sensibility driver, give yourself an opportunity to present, perform or simply engage with others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Balance Sharing and Listening", "description" => "<p>Today, set an intention and begin cultivating an awareness around how much you talk about yourself and ensure you allow others to share as well. Engaging in balanced conversations prevents falling into the weak state of your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver …self-absorption.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Engage in Creative Activities", "description" => "<p>Today, to 'feed' your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver, provide yourself with opportunities to create beauty. Engage in activities that allow you to perform, present, or express without the pressured need for external validation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "VAN", "title" => "Decorate Your Space", "description" => "<p>Today, do one thing to enhance the beauty of your living or working space. Your Aesthetic Sensibility Driver is energized when it creates beauty of any kind.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Create a Daily To-Do List", "description" => "<p>Because you have Perseverance driving you, to help you persevere, make a to-do list today. Write down 3-5 achievable tasks and check off each one as you complete it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Break Projects into Smaller Steps", "description" => "<p>Your Perseverance Driver thrives on completing tasks. Identify one large project and divide it into smaller, manageable tasks to focus on one at a time.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Use Timed Work Sessions", "description" => "<p>To stay optimized and energy-efficient, set a timer for dedicated work sessions today. Work for 40 minutes, then take a 5-minute break. This prevents fatigue and keeps your Perseverance Driver strong.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Know When to Pause", "description" => "<p>Your drive to persevere can lead to stubbornness. If you're stuck today, table the task and return to it later with a fresh perspective.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Tackle Quick Tasks First", "description" => "<p>Your Perseverance Driver thrives on completion. Today, identify 3 tasks taking less than 5 minutes and complete them to build momentum.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Schedule Self-Care", "description" => "<p>Your Perseverance Driver can put off self-care. Today, schedule time for yourself. Choose an activity you enjoy and treat it as an important task.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Manage Stress", "description" => "<p>Because your Perseverance Driver is relentless, stress can build if unmonitored. Remember to open your Energy Centers throughout the day today to manage stress and maintain progress.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Track Achievements", "description" => "<p>Your Perseverance Driver loves progress. At day's end today, review your completed checklist, acknowledging all you got done.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "WIL", "title" => "Communicate Progress", "description" => "<p>Consider updating others on your progress today. Send a brief update to team members or loved ones to foster collaboration. This aligns with your Perseverance Driver's need for completion and acknowledgement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
