            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Fix Instead of Replace", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy makes you incredibly resourceful. Today, find a clever, practical way to fix something that's broken instead of immediately thinking about replacing it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Visit a Thrift Store", "description" => "<p>Your practical nature thrives on a good bargain. Today, or whenever you have the chance, explore a local thrift store. You might find useful items at a fraction of their original cost, perfectly suiting your Copper-Silver Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Reuse Household Items", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy excels at creative solutions. Today, challenge yourself to find new ways to reuse common household items instead of simply throwing them away.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Consider Second-Hand Purchases", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy enables you to find value everywhere. Today, for any upcoming purchases, set an intention to check out consignment stores for clothes or refurbished options for electronics. These choices align with both value and savings.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Upcycle Items at Home", "description" => "<p>Because your Copper-Silver Alchemy is about maximizing use, look around your home today for items you can transform or upcycle, giving them new life instead of buying new.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Participate in Recycling Programs", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy naturally embraces resourcefulness. Today, take a few minutes to research local recycling programs and see how you can participate even more actively.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Compare Generic vs. Name Brands", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy provides a keen eye for value. Today, and regularly when you shop, consciously compare prices of generic brands versus name brands at the grocery store. You'll likely discover significant savings.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Create a Budget-Friendly Meal", "description" => "<p>Today, use ingredients you already have on hand to prepare a satisfying meal. Your practical Copper-Silver Alchemy truly appreciates making the most out of what's available.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "DIY Home Projects", "description" => "<p>Your resourcefulness truly shines in do-it-yourself projects. Today, tackle a small home improvement task using materials you already have. This is a great way to engage your Copper-Silver Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Organize a Swap with Friends", "description" => "<p>To leverage your Copper-Silver Alchemy's value for utility, consider arranging a small swap meet with friends or neighbors to exchange items you no longer need…or simply giving away items to a good cause.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Reduce Waste", "description" => "<p>Today, actively focus on reducing waste by finding new uses for items you'd typically discard, such as repurposing glass jars for storage. This aligns perfectly with your Copper-Silver Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Set a No-Spend Challenge", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy thrives on resourcefulness. Today, challenge yourself to go the entire day without spending any money, creatively using what you already have.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Plan Purchases Carefully", "description" => "<p>Today, before making any purchase, pause and consider if you truly need the item, or if your Copper-Silver Alchemy can find a creative, useful alternative with what you already possess.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Reduce, Reuse, Recycle", "description" => "<p>Today, and moving forward, consciously apply the 'three R's'—reduce, reuse, recycle—to minimize waste and maximize resources. This strategy is highly aligned with your Copper-Silver Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Embrace Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Copper-Silver Alchemy has a natural affinity for the outdoors. Today, make time to spend time in nature, appreciating the simple yet profound beauty of your natural environment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "CS", "title" => "Conserve Energy", "description" => "<p>Today, pay special attention to your energy use at home. Turn off lights in empty rooms and unplug devices when not in use. This practice aligns perfectly with your Copper-Silver Alchemy's appreciation for conservation and efficiency.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Let Fresh Air In", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy deeply thrives in natural environments. Today, if the weather allows, throw open your windows. Let the fresh air and sunlight invigorate your space and your spirit.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Explore New Ways to Connect with Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy provides an innate desire for natural connection. Today, explore a new way to engage with nature, even if just for a few minutes. Set an intention to spend time outdoors at least three times this week.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Practice Grounding", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy offers a profound connection to the earth. Today, if weather permits, walk barefoot on grass or sand. This 'earthing' technique naturally grounds and re-centers you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Recycle and Repurpose", "description" => "<p>Because your Copper Alchemy values utility, embark on a resourceful mission today. Find something old around your home you can cleverly transform into something new and useful.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Embrace Imperfect Produce", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy is comfortably at ease with imperfection. Today, or on your next grocery trip, intentionally choose 'ugly' fruits and vegetables. They're just as nutritious and it's a great way to reduce waste.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Use Natural Cleaning Solutions", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy naturally prefers simple, organic solutions. Today, set an intention that the next time you clean, you'll opt for natural products like vinegar and baking soda.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Choose Eco-Friendly Supplies", "description" => "<p>Your appreciation for sustainability is a core aspect of your Copper Alchemy. Today, and moving forward, consciously choose recycled or eco-friendly supplies when possible.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Dine Outdoors", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy truly thrives in natural settings. Today, make an effort to enjoy a meal outside, even if it's just on your porch, balcony, or in your backyard.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Spend Time with Animals", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy brings a relaxed, accepting attitude towards all creatures. Today, spend some quality, unhurried time with a furry or feathered friend.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Work Near Nature", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy is energized by natural surroundings. If possible today, position your workspace near a window or even take your tasks outside.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Plant Something", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy connects you deeply with the earth's cycles. Today, plant a seed or a small plant, and engage in the simple, nurturing act of fostering its growth.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Take a Nature Walk", "description" => "<p>Embrace your Copper Alchemy by taking a peaceful walk in a natural setting today. Pay close attention to the subtle details of the plants, animals, and the overall environment around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Practice Sustainable Living", "description" => "<p>Today, identify one practical way you can make your lifestyle more sustainable. This could be reducing energy consumption or conserving water, aligning with your Copper Alchemy's values.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Disconnect to Reconnect", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy appreciates simplicity and an unfiltered connection to life. Today, consciously take a break from technology to reconnect with yourself and the natural world around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Create with Natural Materials", "description" => "<p>To engage your Copper Alchemy, today (or sometime this week), use natural materials like wood, stones, or leaves to create something unique – a craft, a simple decoration, or a piece of organic art.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Reflect in Nature", "description" => "<p>Align deeply with your Copper Alchemy today by taking some time to sit quietly in a natural setting, reflecting on your inherent connection with the earth and its rhythms.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Support Eco-Friendly Brands", "description" => "<p>Today, set an intention to prioritize products from brands that genuinely demonstrate a commitment to sustainability and environmental responsibility. These choices truly align with the organic aspects of your Copper Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Support Local Farmers", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy deeply values the earth's natural bounty and local connections. Today, or sometime this week, visit a local farmer's market to support local agriculture and enjoy fresh, direct produce.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "End the Day with Fresh Air", "description" => "<p>Your Copper Alchemy is profoundly connected with nature. Tonight, spend a few moments outside before bedtime, breathing deeply and unwinding under the open sky.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Enjoy a Natural Soundtrack", "description" => "<p>Today, choose to listen to the soothing sounds of nature – bird songs, ocean waves, or rainfall. This aligns with your Copper Alchemy, calming your spirit and enhancing your connection to the natural world.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Walk Instead of Drive", "description" => "<p>If feasible today, choose to walk or bike to your destination instead of driving. This not only reduces your footprint but also allows you to embrace the outdoors, aligning with your Copper Alchemy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Simplify Your Meals", "description" => "<p>Today, prepare a simple, nourishing meal using whole, unprocessed ingredients. Enjoying natural, uncomplicated foods truly aligns with your Copper Alchemy's preference for organic living.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Disconnect from Technology", "description" => "<p>Today, dedicate a specific block of time to unplug from electronic devices. Use this time to relax, reflect, or engage in a hobby that connects you more organically to your surroundings.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "C", "title" => "Observe Wildlife", "description" => "<p>To engage your Copper Alchemy, spend time today simply observing birds, insects, or other small wildlife in your local area. This fosters a deeper appreciation for the natural ecosystem around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],



            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Start Your Day with Movement", "description" => "<p>Because your Moving Energy Center is your 'front door' to your 'vehicle of self,' start your day today with a quick stretch or dynamic body movement to activate your physical connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Walk While Making Calls", "description" => "<p>With your Moving Energy Center as your primary mode of engagement, today, choose to walk while you make phone calls instead of sitting still. This optimizes your information assimilation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Incorporate Movement into Work", "description" => "<p>Since your Moving Energy Center helps you comprehend and assimilate information best while in motion, explore dynamic work setups today. Consider a standing desk, treadmill desk, or balance ball chair to move as you work.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Take Active Breaks", "description" => "<p>As someone who connects best while in motion, take a short, invigorating walk during your lunch break or any other available window of time today. This directly activates your Moving Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Use Fidget Tools", "description" => "<p>Because your Moving Energy Center keeps you engaged and connected to the moment, keep a stress ball or fidget toy at your desk today. Use it to keep your hands in motion while on the phone or contemplating your next task.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Set Reminders to Stretch", "description" => "<p>Since your Moving Energy Center is key to staying connected and engaged, set reminders today to stand up and perform a quick stretch every hour, especially during sedentary activities.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Choose Stairs Over Elevators", "description" => "<p>With your Moving Energy Center as your primary way of connecting with yourself, consciously choose stairs over elevators whenever possible today to naturally incorporate more movement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Doodle While Listening", "description" => "<p>Since your Moving Energy Center connects you deeply to the moment and your interactions, try doodling or drawing while conversing with others on the phone today. This can significantly enhance your focus.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Quick Energy Boost", "description" => "<p>Because your Moving Energy Center helps you connect and engage, when you feel your energy waning today, perform a quick set of jumping jacks or push-ups. This provides an immediate, effective boost.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Park Further Away", "description" => "<p>As someone who connects first through physical motion, make a point today to park your car farther away from entrances. This simple action adds beneficial steps to your day, activating your Moving Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Incorporate Micro-Movements", "description" => "<p>Throughout your day today, incorporate small, subtle movements like toe taps, foot wiggles, or shoulder rolls. This will keep your energy flowing and ensure your Moving Energy Center stays connected.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Wear Comfortable Shoes", "description" => "<p>Because your Moving Energy Center is the primary way you connect with yourself, choose footwear today that genuinely supports easy, continuous movement, making it effortless to stay active throughout your day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Stretch at Your Desk", "description" => "<p>Perform simple, deliberate stretches at your desk today to relieve tension and stay connected to your body. This directly activates the primary manner in which you connect – your Moving Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Take a Dynamic Learning Break", "description" => "<p>When you need to process information or solve a problem today, try taking a short walk or performing some simple body movements. Your Moving Energy Center helps you best comprehend and assimilate while in motion.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Stand While You Think", "description" => "<p>Instead of sitting during moments of contemplation or planning today, try standing up. This simple shift activates your Moving Energy Center, often leading to clearer thoughts and new perspectives.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Active Commute Choice", "description" => "<p>If feasible today, choose an active mode of commute for even a portion of your journey, such as walking or biking. Engaging your Moving Energy Center from the start can set a positive tone.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Use Hand Gestures Intentionally", "description" => "<p>When explaining something or communicating with others today, intentionally use hand gestures. This subtle movement engages your Moving Energy Center, enhancing both your clarity and connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOV", "title" => "Rock or Swivel Your Chair", "description" => "<p>If you find yourself seated for extended periods today, gently rock or swivel in your chair. This small, continuous motion keeps your Moving Energy Center subtly engaged, preventing stagnation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Begin with a Morning Journal", "description" => "<p>Because your Intellectual Energy Center is your 'front door' to your 'vehicle of self,' start your day today by journaling your thoughts, plans, or even a new concept you're pondering.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Explore a New Topic", "description" => "<p>With your Intellectual Energy Center as your primary mode of connection, dedicate focused time today to researching a subject you've always been curious about. Dive deep into understanding.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Reflect Before Bedtime", "description" => "<p>Since your Intellectual Energy Center thrives on making sense of information, take a few minutes tonight to reflect on what new insights or understandings you've gained today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Keep a Question Log", "description" => "<p>As someone who connects first through your Intellectual Energy Center, keep a log of questions that arise throughout your day today. Set an intention over the next few days to seek their answers through research or by asking informed individuals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Teach Someone Something New", "description" => "<p>Because your Intellectual Energy Center is your primary way of engaging, make it a point today to explain a new concept or idea to someone else. Articulating it will deepen your own understanding.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Identify Knowledge Gaps", "description" => "<p>Today, take a moment to precisely identify an area where you need more information and form a clear plan to acquire that knowledge. Each new understanding activates your Intellectual Energy Center, connecting you in the moment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Learn a New Word", "description" => "<p>Set aside 10 minutes today to learn a new word and consciously practice using it in conversation or writing. This direct action 'opens the door' to your primary way of connecting and communicating: your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Create a Curiosity List", "description" => "<p>Your Intellectual Energy Center is inherently drawn to deeper understanding. Begin a comprehensive list of topics that genuinely pique your curiosity and spend a few focused minutes exploring one of them today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Engage in Deep Conversation", "description" => "<p>Seek out a truly meaningful conversation with someone today about a topic that deeply interests you. This deliberate engagement will 'open the door' to your Intellectual Energy Center and foster profound connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Answer Your Own Questions", "description" => "<p>Your Intellectual Energy Center craves answers. Today, actively look up the answer to at least one specific question you've had recently. Make this precise inquiry a consistent daily practice.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Attend a Webinar or Lecture", "description" => "<p>Today, set a clear intention to research and register for a future online webinar, lecture, or conference on a subject that genuinely fascinates you. This commitment to learning is deeply nurturing for your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Read a Challenging Book", "description" => "<p>Your Intellectual Energy Center is naturally drawn to expanding knowledge. Choose a book that genuinely challenges your current thinking and dedicate focused time to reading it today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Create a Reading List", "description" => "<p>One powerful way to 'open the door' to your Intellectual Energy Center is through reading. Compile a precise list of books you'd like to read and actively start with one today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Attend a Workshop", "description" => "<p>Today, dedicate time to researching workshops, masterminds, conferences, or seminars that truly intrigue you. Make a concrete decision to sign up for one. Any opportunity to enhance your knowledge in a specific area is nurturing for your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Listen to an Educational Podcast", "description" => "<p>While commuting or during downtime today, intentionally listen to a podcast that educates and inspires. This focused activity helps you stay connected as it opens your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Subscribe to a Thought-Provoking Newsletter", "description" => "<p>Today, consider subscribing to a newsletter that consistently delivers interesting, intellectually stimulating articles directly to your inbox. Because you connect with your world first through your Intellectual Energy Center, knowledge is intrinsically attractive to you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Solve a Puzzle or Brain Teaser", "description" => "<p>Engage your Intellectual Energy Center directly today by tackling a complex puzzle, crossword, or brain teaser. This focused mental exercise is one way to 'open the door' to this primary Energy Center in you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Research a Historical Event", "description" => "<p>Pick a historical event or period that you've always found intriguing today and spend some dedicated time researching its details and broader context. Your Intellectual Energy Center thrives on understanding origins.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Create a Concept Map", "description" => "<p>To deepen your comprehension, today, take a topic you're learning about and create a visual concept map or diagram. This spatial organization helps your Intellectual Energy Center make connections.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Engage in a Friendly Debate", "description" => "<p>Seek out an opportunity today for a friendly, intellectual debate with someone about a topic you both care about. This sharpens your reasoning and broadens your perspective, engaging your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INT", "title" => "Visit an Online Museum/Gallery", "description" => "<p>Today, explore an online museum or virtual gallery tour related to an area of interest. Immersing yourself in curated knowledge activates your Intellectual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Engage in Physical Affection", "description" => "<p>Because your Emotional Energy Center connects deeply through physical touch, today, engage in deliberate acts of affection, such as a warm hug, holding hands, or gently petting a beloved pet. These actions directly open the door to your emotional connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Prioritize Face-to-Face Interactions", "description" => "<p>You connect first with yourself, your environment, and others through your Emotional Energy Center. Today, consciously make time for in-person conversations or brief social gatherings to nurture your vital connections.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Offer Emotional Support", "description" => "<p>Since you primarily connect and communicate through your Emotional Energy Center, engage in a genuine act of kindness today by offering emotional support to someone through connected gestures or heartfelt words.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Begin a Gratitude Practice", "description" => "<p>Start a gratitude journal today by precisely noting three things you are deeply thankful for that involve a living connection. Make this a daily practice to reinforce positive emotions and strengthen your emotional bonds.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Engage in Meaningful Conversations", "description" => "<p>Go beyond superficial small talk today by initiating deeper, more meaningful conversations that explore emotions and shared experiences. This directly aligns with your Emotional Energy Center and fosters profound relationships.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Share Common Interests", "description" => "<p>Use common interests as genuine conversation starters today to engage in shared experiences with others. This enhances your emotional connections and effectively 'opens the door' to your Emotional Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Collaborate with Others", "description" => "<p>Actively look for opportunities to work together with others on shared interests or projects today. This allows you to 'open the door' to your Emotional Energy Center, as you feel most connected and engaged in the presence of others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Perform Acts of Kindness", "description" => "<p>Engage in specific, random acts of kindness today, such as offering a sincere compliment or holding a door open for someone. Consciously connecting with others in this way deeply connects for you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Extend Social Invitations", "description" => "<p>Today, intentionally invite someone to join you for a simple social activity like coffee or a casual lunch. Nurturing these direct emotional connections activates your Emotional Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Reconnect with Old Friends", "description" => "<p>Today, reach out to an old friend or family member you haven't spoken to in a while to rekindle your connection. This act directly 'opens the door' to your Emotional Energy Center and optimizes your energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Spend Time with Loved Ones", "description" => "<p>Dedicate quality, intentional time today to be truly present with loved ones. Whether it's deep conversation, holding hands, sharing laughter, or simply being together, all these activities activate your Emotional Energy Center and nurture your connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Engage in Group Activities", "description" => "<p>Today, spend some time considering what types of group activities or community events genuinely resonate with you. Actively engaging with others in these settings 'opens the door' to your Emotional Energy Center and fosters your deepest connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Express Emotions Healthily", "description" => "<p>Today, find a healthy way to express your emotions, whether through journaling, talking to a trusted friend, or engaging in a creative outlet. This direct emotional expression empowers your Emotional Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Watch a Heartwarming Video", "description" => "<p>When you have a few minutes today, choose to watch a quick, heartwarming video – perhaps of animals, children, or genuine human connection. This simple act can gently activate your Emotional Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Make Meaningful Eye Contact", "description" => "<p>Today, during your interactions, consciously make and hold genuine eye contact with others. This simple yet powerful gesture directly engages your Emotional Energy Center and deepens connection.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Connect with Nature (Living Things)", "description" => "<p>Take a moment today to connect with living things in nature. This could be watering your plants, observing local wildlife, or simply sitting near a tree. Your Emotional Energy Center connects with the life force around you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "EM", "title" => "Send a Heartfelt Message", "description" => "<p>Today, send a heartfelt text, email, or physical note to someone special, simply to let them know you're thinking of them. This act of sending positive emotion nourishes your Emotional Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Start Your Day with Sensory Pleasures", "description" => "<p>Because your Instinctual Energy Center is your 'front door' to your 'vehicle of self,' spend extra time bathing today. Use scented soaps, bath salts, really hot (or cold) water, or play your favorite music to set a truly connecting, sensory tone for the day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Wear Your Favorite Color", "description" => "<p>You connect first with yourself, your environment, and others through your Instinctual Energy Center. Today, intentionally wear your favorite color and keenly notice the immediate, uplifting energy boost it provides.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Choose Visually Appealing Meals", "description" => "<p>The primary way you connect and communicate is through your Instinctual Energy Center. Today, choose meals that are not only delicious but also deeply visually appealing. Savor the aesthetic of your food.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Observe Calming Scenes", "description" => "<p>Because your Instinctual Energy Center is sensitive to its surroundings, take focused time today to observe your environment and consciously find calming, photo-worthy scenes that soothe your senses.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Wear Comfortable Clothing", "description" => "<p>You connect first with yourself and others through your Instinctual Energy Center. Today, choose clothing made from fabrics that feel exceptionally comfortable and pleasant against your skin.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Create a Pleasant Atmosphere", "description" => "<p>Today, light your favorite candle, incense, diffuse an essential oil or let fresh outside air in to intentionally create a pleasant atmosphere that deeply appeals to your senses and opens your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Enjoy a Sensory Ritual", "description" => "<p>The primary way you connect and communicate is through your Instinctual Energy Center. Today, perform a simple sensory ritual: apply your favorite lotion, oil, or balm, taking time to inhale its scent deeply before application.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Watch a Sunrise or Sunset", "description" => "<p>Set a deliberate intention today to watch either a sunrise or a sunset. Immerse yourself in this natural beauty to profoundly connect with your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Trust Your Gut Instincts", "description" => "<p>Because you have direct access to your gut instincts, consciously listen to them today (and every day) when making decisions, provided you are not fatigued or overly stressed. This activates your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Surround Yourself with Comfort", "description" => "<p>Today, choose clothing that feels exceptionally good on your skin. This simple act directly connects you with your environment through your Instinctual Energy Center, enhancing your comfort and presence.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Savor Your Food Slowly", "description" => "<p>The 'door' to your Instinctual Energy Center opens by activating any of your five senses. Today, make a conscious effort to savor each bite during meals, deeply appreciating the flavors, textures, and aromas.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Practice Deep Breathing", "description" => "<p>Take intentional moments throughout your day today to breathe deeply, focusing entirely on the sensation of air entering and leaving your body. As you are Instinctually centered, this is a purposefully connecting activity for you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Engage with Nature", "description" => "<p>Spend focused time outdoors today, actively feeling the breeze, truly seeing the vibrant sights, and deeply enjoying the natural sounds around you. This sensory-filled activity directly connects you with your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Listen to Soothing Music", "description" => "<p>Today, play music that truly relaxes or energizes you, precisely aligning with your current needs. This deliberate choice will 'open the door' to your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Enjoy a Warm Beverage", "description" => "<p>Today, slowly sip on a warm cup of tea, coffee or other tasty beverage, focusing intensely on the taste, the warmth, and the comforting aroma it brings. Activating your senses in this way will make you feel profoundly connected.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Use a Comfortable Chair", "description" => "<p>Today, consciously assess the chair you spend the most time in. Ensure it is truly comfortable and supportive. If not, set a firm intention to obtain a new chair or special cushions, as your Instinctual Energy Center is sensitive to discomfort, which can distract you from being present.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Wear Soft Fabrics", "description" => "<p>Because you are Instinctually centered, today (and every day), prioritize choosing clothing made from exceptionally soft fabrics that feel genuinely comforting and pleasant against your skin.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Enjoy a Foot or Hand Massage", "description" => "<p>Set aside 10 minutes today to give yourself a foot massage, or use a massage tool to deeply relax and connect with your body. Alternatively, massage your hands with lotion, focusing on the tactile sensation. All these activities help 'open the door' to your Instinctual Energy Center, leaving you feeling more profoundly connected.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Mindful Observation of Art/Beauty", "description" => "<p>Today, spend a few minutes mindfully observing a piece of art, a beautiful photograph, or any object you find aesthetically pleasing. Allow your Instinctual Energy Center to connect with its visual harmony.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Engage with Pleasurable Scents", "description" => "<p>Throughout your day today, consciously seek out and savor pleasing smells – perhaps a fresh flower, a favorite herb, or a natural essential oil. This direct sensory input deeply nourishes your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Savor a Texture", "description" => "<p>Today, intentionally touch and feel an object with an interesting or comforting texture – a smooth stone, a soft blanket, or even the grain of a wooden surface. Allowing your sense of touch to engage activates your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Consciously Hydrate", "description" => "<p>Today, focus on the sensory experience of drinking water or a healthy beverage. Notice the cool or refreshing sensation, hydrating your body and satisfying your Instinctual Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "INS", "title" => "Create a Visually Soothing Space", "description" => "<p>Before bed tonight, take a moment to ensure your bedroom is visually soothing. Your Instinctual Energy Center thrives in harmonious environments, preparing you for restful sleep.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Engage in Solution-Based Discussions", "description" => "<p>Your Positive Perception of Life naturally steers conversations toward constructive solutions. When discussing challenges today, consciously propose potential solutions to foster truly productive dialogue.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Share Your Perspective", "description" => "<p>Others deeply benefit from your ability to highlight the positive. Sharing your perspective helps cultivate a supportive environment. Today, offer mentorship or guidance to someone facing a challenge, sharing your unique, positive viewpoint.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Celebrate Progress", "description" => "<p>Your Positive Perception of Life thrives on recognizing achievements. Reflecting on progress powerfully boosts your energy. Today, write down a specific small victory from your day and celebrate it, no matter how minor it may seem.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Inspire Through Positivity", "description" => "<p>Your ability to find solutions makes you a guiding light. Use this to uplift others around you. Today, share a genuinely uplifting story or positive insight with a colleague or friend to inspire their perspective.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Amplify Your 'What’s Working' Perception", "description" => "<p>You naturally focus on what's working first. Leveraging this Positive Perception of Life can inspire others and maintain your momentum. Today, list three specific successes you anticipate achieving in the near future, cultivating an energy of proactive positivity.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Visualize Success", "description" => "<p>Visualizing positive outcomes strongly reinforces your natural focus on potential solutions. Spend 10 minutes today vividly visualizing a successful outcome for a current project or goal, tapping into your Positive Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Expand Your Perspective", "description" => "<p>Recognizing and valuing different perceptions broadens your understanding and deepens your impact. Today, spend time speaking with someone who naturally views things differently than your Positive Perception of Life, and listen without offering solutions initially.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Activate Your Positive Perception of Life with Gratitude", "description" => "<p>Gratitude reinforces your Positive Perception of Life, creating a feedback loop of more of what you desire. Before bed tonight, jot down three specific things you're genuinely grateful for today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Prioritize What’s Working", "description" => "<p>Focusing on what is effective allows you to optimize your workflow and maintain energy. Today, clearly identify and double down on the tasks or strategies that are currently most successful for you, leveraging your Positive Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Counter Energy That Doesn’t Come Across As Positive", "description" => "<p>While you have a Positive Perception of Life, you may encounter others today who operate from a more Negative Perception. This simply means they'll express what's not working more. When you encounter these individuals, today, prepare yourself to maintain your positive perspective by taking a deep breath and mentally listing three positive aspects of the situation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Seek Out Uplifting Content", "description" => "<p>To consistently feed your Positive Perception of Life, today, intentionally seek out content that is inspiring or uplifting – a podcast, an article, or a video that focuses on success and potential.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Reframe a Minor Setback", "description" => "<p>When you encounter a minor setback today, consciously reframe it. Your Positive Perception of Life allows you to immediately look for the lesson or the opportunity within the challenge, rather than dwelling on the problem.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Find the 'Win' in Every Interaction", "description" => "<p>Today, at the end of each significant interaction, consciously identify at least one 'win' or positive takeaway, no matter how small. This strengthens your Positive Perception of Life's natural inclination to find what's working.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PV", "title" => "Offer a Positive Suggestion", "description" => "<p>When you're part of a discussion about a challenge today, make sure to be the one who offers at least one concrete, positive suggestion for a path forward, demonstrating your Positive Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Present Problems As Constructive Feedback", "description" => "<p>Today, consciously practice framing your critical perceptions as constructive feedback. Your ability to spot flaws is invaluable when presented in a way others can readily accept and act upon.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Reinforce Your Problem-Solving Skills", "description" => "<p>Today, specifically acknowledge one problem you've successfully solved recently. This reinforces your problem-solving skills and reminds you of your inherent ability to overcome challenges – a direct reflection of your natural Negative Perception of Life that identifies what’s not working first. Remember, your ability to identify problems is an essential ingredient to the whole picture.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Reserve Time For Problem-Solving", "description" => "<p>Set aside dedicated time today for a focused problem-solving session where you can deeply address issues you've identified. This allows you to productively access your problem-oriented aspect of your Negative Perception of Life without overwhelming others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Practice Active Listening", "description" => "<p>Practice active listening today when others are sharing their ideas or experiences. Your natural inclination to identify problems can be highly effective when tempered by fully understanding others' perspectives before offering a critique.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Practice Reframing", "description" => "<p>Today, practice reframing a negative perception you might have in the moment into questions that invite discussion. For example, instead of stating 'This won't work,' try asking 'How might we overcome the challenges in this approach?' This leverages your Negative Perception of Life for collaborative progress.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Volunteer As 'Devil’s Advocate'", "description" => "<p>When faced with a decision today, volunteer to play the role of 'devil's advocate.' This allows you to utilize your natural inclination to spot potential problems in a way that's expected and valued by others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Engage in a Brainstorming Session", "description" => "<p>Engage in a focused brainstorming session with yourself today to strategically uncover problems. Your analytical mind, driven by your Negative Perception of Life, thrives on creating comprehensive plans to address problems.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Balance Your Critical Perceptions", "description" => "<p>When interacting with people who seem to share what’s working first, practice balancing your critical perceptions with genuine acknowledgments of what they share today. This can help create more harmonious relationships while still utilizing your unique Negative Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Challenge Yourself to Find Patterns or Inconsistencies", "description" => "<p>When reviewing data or managing finances today (or in the future), challenge yourself to actively find patterns or inconsistencies that others might miss. Your natural ability to uncover errors, a strength of your Negative Perception of Life, keeps accuracy consistent and makes you highly dependable.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Honor Your 'What’s Not Working' Approach", "description" => "<p>Seek out activities today that directly honor the value you offer in your innate ability to identify and address what's not working. Activities that allow you to fix or 'right a perceived wrong' will powerfully access your Negative Perception of Life as you solve the problem at hand.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Acknowledge Your 'Fix-It' Nature", "description" => "<p>End your day today by specifically acknowledging one thing you successfully 'fixed' or improved. This reinforces the value of your innate ability, driven by your Negative Perception of Life, to address what’s not working and make it right.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Troubleshoot Inefficiencies", "description" => "<p>Identify one specific aspect of your day (at work or at home) that could be optimized today. Your natural inclination to troubleshoot inefficiencies, a key strength of your Negative Perception of Life, can lead to significant, tangible improvements.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Acknowledge Your Problem-Oriented Mindset", "description" => "<p>Today, consciously acknowledge the immense value of your problem-oriented mindset. Recognize that identifying issues early, a function of your Negative Perception of Life, can prevent much larger problems down the line, much like a surgeon pinpointing what needs repair for a successful outcome.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Harness Your Critical Abilities", "description" => "<p>Your natural focus on problems is a powerful strength for identifying areas of improvement. Use it constructively. Today, choose one aspect of your day that feels inefficient and systematically brainstorm potential improvements, leveraging your Negative Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Create a 'Problem-Solving Playbook'", "description" => "<p>Today, begin to document common problems you encounter and effective solutions you've discovered. Your Negative Perception of Life can build an invaluable resource for yourself and others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Debrief Challenges with Clarity", "description" => "<p>When discussing a past challenge today, concisely articulate what went wrong and precisely why. Your Negative Perception of Life provides the clarity needed for accurate debriefing and learning.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Offer Specific, Actionable Critique", "description" => "<p>If asked for feedback today, provide specific, actionable critiques. Your Negative Perception of Life's ability to spot flaws is most valuable when it leads directly to improvement.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Research Potential Pitfalls", "description" => "<p>Before starting a new initiative today (or in the future), dedicate a short time to researching potential pitfalls or common mistakes. Your Negative Perception of Life is an asset in proactive risk mitigation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "NE", "title" => "Identify Missing Elements", "description" => "<p>When reviewing a plan or project today, actively identify any missing elements or overlooked details. Your Negative Perception of Life excels at completing the whole picture by highlighting gaps.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Facilitate Balanced Discussions", "description" => "<p>Because your Neutral Perception of Life provides the natural ability to perceive both what works and what doesn't, you can effectively mediate and bring harmony to conversations by highlighting diverse viewpoints. Step into a mediating role if the opportunity arises today, aiming to bridge differing perspectives.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Honor Both Sides", "description" => "<p>Your unique ability to perceive both the positives and negatives can help balance perspectives. When faced with a situation today (or any day), consciously note one specific positive and one specific challenge before deciding your approach.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Acknowledge The Pause As You Weigh Both Perspectives", "description" => "<p>Your tendency to consider both what isn’t working and what is working is natural for your Neutral Perception of Life. Today, notice and honor 'the pause' as you assess a current situation, identifying both its strengths and weaknesses before making a decision.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Embrace Your Neutral Stance", "description" => "<p>Your neutral stance inherently leads to exceptionally well-rounded decisions. Spend 10 minutes today journaling about a recent event, specifically considering both what went well and what could have been improved, engaging your Neutral Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Express Your Perceptions", "description" => "<p>Your insights bring invaluable clarity to others. Sharing them thoughtfully enhances collective understanding. Share a balanced observation in a meeting or discussion today, consciously aiming to present both sides of the situation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Support Others’ Perceptions", "description" => "<p>Having a Neutral Perception of Life helps you quickly understand others’ views and offer truly balanced support. Today, validate someone’s experience by specifically acknowledging both their challenges and their triumphs.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Reflect Without Judging", "description" => "<p>Identifying both positive and negative aspects of your day is natural for your Neutral Perception of Life. Consciously identifying these aspects without attaching judgment can cultivate profound peace. Practice a non-judgmental observation of your day today, simply noting what was positive and what was challenging.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Foster The Objective Perspective", "description" => "<p>Your natural ability to perceive both what works and what doesn’t gives you effortless access to objectivity. Notice how you engage in conversation today by consciously considering the objective, whole-picture approach your Neutral Perception of Life provides.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Mediate a Small Disagreement", "description" => "<p>If a minor disagreement arises today, offer to mediate. Your Neutral Perception of Life makes you uniquely suited to help parties see each other's viewpoints and find common ground.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Review Decisions from All Angles", "description" => "<p>Before making a significant decision today, intentionally list the pros and cons, but also consider the potential risks and opportunities. This holistic review leverages your Neutral Perception of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "N", "title" => "Provide Balanced Feedback", "description" => "<p>When giving feedback to someone today, ensure you provide a balanced perspective, acknowledging both strengths and areas for improvement. This aligns with your Neutral Perception of Life's comprehensive view.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Start Your Day with High-Energy Activities", "description" => "<p>Your vast energy needs early, purposeful activation to optimize your day. Begin your day today by expending some of your energy in a larger activity (or several activities) that allows you to release excess energy, leveraging your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Schedule Time for Mindful Pauses", "description" => "<p>Your naturally high energy can lead to overstimulation. Deliberate pauses throughout your day can help maintain internal harmony. Set reminders today for three 5-10 minute 'step away' sessions where you completely stop and engage in deep breathing or step outside for fresh air.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Engage in Creative Projects", "description" => "<p>Your exceptional energy level profoundly supports expansive thinking. Creative outlets can help harness this effectively. Dedicate 30 minutes today to a creative activity that genuinely excites you, like drawing, brainstorming, or crafting, utilizing your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Emphasize Connection without Overpowering", "description" => "<p>Recognize that others might not match your immense energy level, so approach interactions with this acute awareness. Today, practice active listening during conversations and fine-tune your energy to your audience to ensure your enthusiasm doesn't overshadow others.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Incorporate Restorative Activities", "description" => "<p>Balancing your high-energy state with restorative practices is crucial for sustained optimization. End your day today with 15 minutes of gentle stretching or a quiet activity to unwind, allowing your Above Excellent Energy Pool to restore effectively.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Practice Energy Awareness", "description" => "<p>Staying acutely aware of how your energy impacts others fosters better connections. Observe your energy in social settings today and adjust to maintain harmony with those around you, demonstrating mastery over your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Plan Low-Intensity Time Slots", "description" => "<p>Not every task should demand peak energy. Today, intentionally schedule several lower-energy activities to provide crucial recharge periods for your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Support Others with Your Energy", "description" => "<p>Your abundant energy can be profoundly inspiring. Use it purposefully to uplift others. Today, offer to assist a colleague or friend who could genuinely benefit from your extra bandwidth.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Reflect on Energy Expenditure", "description" => "<p>Self-reflection is vital to maintain an optimal energy balance. Because you possess such 'big energy,' you must be keenly aware of how efficiently you are utilizing your energy. Before you go to sleep tonight, spend 5 minutes thoughtfully considering your day's energy expenditure. Jot down notes if adjustments are needed for tomorrow.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Prioritize Your Needs", "description" => "<p>Your 'big energy' requires conscious, precise care for your physical body to remain optimized. Today, identify one specific physiological need (e.g., specific hydration, targeted nutrition, or supplementation) and rigorously meet it to ensure you maintain peak energy efficiency for your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Engage in a Morning Energy Release", "description" => "<p>Before your main engagements today, expend some targeted energy in a physical activity like a quick run, vigorous stretching, or a burst of dancing. This proactive release optimizes your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Delegate High-Energy Tasks Judiciously", "description" => "<p>While you have vast energy, today, practice delegating specific high-energy tasks that might be better suited for others or that would benefit from a different perspective. This frees your Above Excellent Energy Pool for strategic use.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Mindful Communication of Enthusiasm", "description" => "<p>When sharing your enthusiasm today, consciously modulate your delivery to match your audience's energy levels. This ensures your Above Excellent Energy Pool inspires without overwhelming.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Practice 'Energy Sealing' Rituals", "description" => "<p>At key transitions today (e.g., before meetings, after intense work), perform a quick 'energy sealing' ritual like a few deep breaths or a moment of stillness. This helps contain and manage your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AE", "title" => "Seek Out Passive Inspiration", "description" => "<p>To balance your active energy, today, intentionally seek out passive forms of inspiration, like listening to an audiobook or watching a documentary that sparks thought without requiring active expenditure from your Above Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Embrace Your Natural Energy Efficiency", "description" => "<p>Your Excellent Energy Pool means you can operate with high productivity. Today, plan your most demanding task when it precisely aligns with your most productive trait for that task. Remind yourself of the nature of your top three traits and execute the task when the optimal trait is most naturally available and can best support it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Stay Hydrated", "description" => "<p>Proper hydration is fundamental to maintaining your exceptional Excellent Energy Pool. Ensure you drink plenty of good, pure water throughout your day today.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Schedule Quick Breaks", "description" => "<p>Even with your high energy, short, strategic breaks are vital for maintaining mental sharpness. Plan three 15-minute breaks throughout your day today for simple stretches, deep breathing, or a quick walk to recharge your Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Share Your Energy Efficiently", "description" => "<p>You possess a substantial Excellent Energy Pool to expend each day, meaning you can easily use some of your energy to support others without overextending. Today, genuinely offer to assist someone who could benefit from your extra bandwidth.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Engage in Evening Reflection", "description" => "<p>You have an Excellent Energy Pool to work with daily, and reviewing your day helps sustain energy mastery. End your day today with a precise 5-minute reflection on how you managed your energy and what minor adjustments could be made for tomorrow.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Listen to Your Body", "description" => "<p>Even though you have a significant Excellent Energy Pool to expend, your body knows when to signal rest. Check in with how you feel throughout your day today and adjust your activities as needed, honoring your body's wisdom.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Connect With Yourself More Deeply By Engaging In A Lifestyle Activity", "description" => "<p>Doing what you love helps maintain high energy. Set aside 20-30 minutes today for a 'lifestyle' type activity that deeply engages your primary Energy Center. This extended engagement, aligned with your primary Energy Center, nurtures your Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Optimize Your Sleep Routine", "description" => "<p>To sustain your Excellent Energy Pool, prioritize consistent, quality sleep. Today, ensure you go to bed and wake up at roughly the same time, even on weekends, creating a stable rhythm for your body.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Fuel with Nutrient-Dense Foods", "description" => "<p>Your Excellent Energy Pool benefits from consistent, high-quality fuel. Today, make conscious choices to include nutrient-dense foods in every meal and snack to support sustained energy levels.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Prioritize Complex Tasks Strategically", "description" => "<p>With your Excellent Energy Pool, you have the capacity for demanding work. Today, strategically schedule your most complex tasks during your natural peak productivity times to maximize efficiency and leverage your energy. Review how your top three Traits unfold for you each day and notice which Traits align best with which tasks.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Engage in Social Connections That Recharge You", "description" => "<p>Your Excellent Energy Pool thrives on healthy interactions. Today, intentionally connect with individuals or groups that genuinely energize and uplift you, rather than drain your resources.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "E", "title" => "Review Your Weekly Schedule for Balance", "description" => "<p>Before the day ends today, take a few minutes to review your upcoming weekly schedule. Identify opportunities to proactively build in balance between work, rest, and personal enjoyment to maintain your Excellent Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Consciously Manage Energy Flow", "description" => "<p>With an Average Energy Pool, it’s important to be aware of conserving and efficiently using your energy. Today, review the 'nature' of your top three traits and your two drivers. Precisely identify the best time of day to complete your tasks based on when particular traits are most available for you and how the task aligns with one (or both) of your drivers.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Include Energizing Breaks", "description" => "<p>You have an Average Energy Pool to expend each day. Breaks are vital to rejuvenate your energy throughout the day. Today, try engaging in 90-minute blocks of work with focused 15-minute breaks in between. During breaks, do something truly nurturing, like a short walk outside, a nutritious snack, or targeted breathing exercises.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Monitor Fatigue Signals", "description" => "<p>Recognizing early signs of fatigue is essential to recharge before depletion. If you start to feel tired today, immediately pause what you're doing and activate quick strategies to open each of your four Energy Centers (in the order they appear in your Core Stats). These quick actions will help rejuvenate your Average Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Optimize Nutrition", "description" => "<p>A balanced diet is foundational for consistent energy levels. Today, make a conscious effort to include a nutrient-dense snack with protein to maintain steady energy for your Average Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Thankfulness", "description" => "<p>Expressing authentic thanks for the gifts in your life genuinely contributes to the rejuvenation of your energy levels. Today, take a deliberate break to write down three specific things you're thankful for. Set an intention to add to this list every day and read through it at least once daily to reset your energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Stay Hydrated", "description" => "<p>Nurturing your physical body fundamentally supports keeping your Average Energy Pool at its optimum. Water is crucial for energy by keeping your body hydrated and functioning well. Today, drink a glass of pure water every two hours and consciously notice how you feel by the end of the day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Plan for an Evening Wind-Down", "description" => "<p>A calming evening routine is critical to recharge your Average Energy Pool for the next day. Dedicate 20 minutes before bed tonight to relaxing activities like deep breathing, listening to calming music, reading something inspiring, doing light stretches, or cuddling with a significant person or pet.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Check in with Your Energy Levels", "description" => "<p>Regularly assessing your energy is key to optimizing your activities. Take a moment today to precisely evaluate your current energy and adjust the number or intensity of activities you are committing to. This intelligent management of your Average Energy Pool is a great way to remain energy efficient.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Prioritize Sleep Hygiene", "description" => "<p>Consistent, quality sleep is paramount for maintaining your Average Energy Pool. Today, focus on one aspect of your sleep hygiene – ensuring a dark, quiet room, or avoiding screens before bed.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Avoid Energy Drains", "description" => "<p>Identify activities, people, or environments that noticeably drain your energy. Today, consciously limit exposure to one such drain, preserving your Average Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Pack Nutritious Snacks", "description" => "<p>To prevent energy dips, today, proactively pack 1-2 nutritious snacks to have on hand. This ensures consistent fuel for your Energy Pool (which is currently Average) throughout your day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Gentle Movement Breaks", "description" => "<p>During periods of prolonged stillness today, take short, gentle movement breaks – a quick walk to the kitchen or a few arm circles – to keep your Average Energy Pool flowing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "A", "title" => "Set Realistic Expectations", "description" => "<p>With an Average Energy Pool, it's crucial to set realistic expectations for what you can accomplish today. Prioritize quality over quantity to avoid burnout and maintain sustainable energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Prioritize Restorative Practices", "description" => "<p>With a Fair Energy Pool, self-care is not optional; it is essential. Set aside 20 minutes today for a deeply calming activity that 'opens the door' to your primary (first) Energy Center, as listed on your dashboard. This deliberate act is essential for your well-being.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Limit High-Demand Activities", "description" => "<p>Because you are currently working with a Fair Energy Pool, protecting your energy means carefully choosing how it’s used. Today, explicitly identify and postpone non-urgent, high-energy tasks until you feel more significantly restored.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Seek Out Nature", "description" => "<p>Connecting with nature is a powerful way to replenish your Fair Energy Pool. Spend 15 minutes outside today, whether walking gently or simply sitting in the sun, allowing the natural environment to soothe you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Engage in Gentle Movement", "description" => "<p>Light physical activities like stretching can genuinely combat fatigue. Today, when you begin to feel fatigue, practice gentle stretches for 5 minutes to loosen up and subtly rejuvenate your Fair Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Hydrate and Nourish", "description" => "<p>Because your energy is currently Fair, keeping your body consistently nourished is paramount for energy recovery. Today, when you notice fatigue creeping in, proactively prepare and consume a nutrient-rich snack and drink a full glass of pure water.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Use Breathing Exercises", "description" => "<p>Controlled breathing is a potent tool to restore energy and reduce stress. Today, and whenever you feel your energy waning, practice three minutes of deep, intentional breathing to support your Fair Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Listen to Your Body", "description" => "<p>Because you are currently operating with a Fair Energy Pool, honoring your body’s signals is critical to prevent further depletion. Today, as soon as you notice any signs of mental or physical fatigue, immediately take a 20-minute break and activate one of the following: be in nature (walk barefoot in grass or lean against a tree), access nature sounds via an app with eyes closed, or sit in a comfortable chair with an eye mask.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Schedule Enjoyable Activities", "description" => "<p>Consistently doing things you genuinely enjoy helps replenish energy. Plan 30 minutes of enjoyable downtime today by activating a 'lifestyle' type activity that engages your primary Energy Center. This dedicated time deeply nurtures your Fair Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Reach Out for Support", "description" => "<p>You currently have a Fair Energy Pool, making it a wise time to seek assistance from a trusted healthcare practitioner. Often, this energy state indicates a deeper physical issue. Set a clear intention today to research the best practitioner for you, or schedule an appointment with your current one.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Reassess Priorities", "description" => "<p>With the Fair Energy Pool you are currently working with, focusing solely on essential tasks is crucial for managing energy effectively. Today, rigorously reevaluate your to-do list and commit only to what is truly necessary.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Practice 'Energy Banking'", "description" => "<p>Today, identify one activity you genuinely enjoy that gives you energy (e.g., listening to a favorite song, a few minutes of quiet). Consciously 'bank' this energy by engaging in it for a few minutes. This proactive approach helps build your Fair Energy Pool.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Gentle Self-Compassion", "description" => "<p>Recognize that your energy is currently Fair, and practice self-compassion today. Avoid pushing yourself unnecessarily or feeling guilty for needing rest. Your Fair Energy Pool benefits from being kind to yourself.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Mindful Consumption of Information", "description" => "<p>Your Fair Energy Pool can be easily overwhelmed by too much input. Today, be mindful of the news, social media, and other information sources. Choose to consume only what is necessary, minimizing mental fatigue.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "F", "title" => "Create a 'Rest Corner'", "description" => "<p>Today, if you don't already have one, designate a specific spot in your home as a 'rest corner' – a comfortable, quiet place where you can retreat for short periods to recharge your Fair Energy Pool without distraction.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Embrace Your 'Test Drives' with Openness", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life is about exploring various motivations and interests. 'Test driving' different activities helps you discover what genuinely resonates. Today, try something new—a hobby, a sport, or a skill. Reflect on how it makes you feel and whether it energizes or deeply interests you. If it does, set an intention to pursue it further!</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Balance Independence with Guidance", "description" => "<p>While it's natural for you in your current Interval of Life to have a desire for more independence and less reliance on parental figures, maintaining a healthy balance by seeking guidance when needed can prevent missteps. When faced with a challenging choice today, reach out to a parent, trusted adult, or mentor for their invaluable perspective before deciding.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Identify Your Emerging Talents", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Your Life is when your unique talents begin to become more evident. Recognizing them early builds confidence and provides clear direction. Today, reflect on which activities come most naturally to you and consistently receive positive feedback from others. Set an intention to participate more in those specific activities.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Cultivate Self-Worth Beyond Validation", "description" => "<p>The desire for external validation, especially in relationships, can be intense during your particular Interval of Life. Understanding your inherent value without needing constant affirmation from others profoundly strengthens your self-esteem. Spend a few minutes today listing qualities about yourself that you genuinely appreciate, entirely independent of others' opinions. Post your list where you'll see it every day and commit to adding to it and rereading it at least once daily.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Foster a Growth Mindset", "description" => "<p>Mistakes are an inevitable part of your current Interval of Life, but viewing them as valuable opportunities for growth rather than outright failures supports lifelong learning and resilience. Today, recall a recent mistake, write down one specific lesson you learned from it, and clarify how it can specifically help you in the future.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Practice Self-Reflection Regularly", "description" => "<p>With the rapid change and new experiences present in your current Interval of Life, taking time to reflect consistently helps maintain a clear sense of self. Set aside 10 minutes at the end of your day today to consider what you genuinely enjoyed, what truly challenged you, and what valuable lessons you learned.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Practice Pausing Before Decision-Making", "description" => "<p>With so many choices and internal 'voices' driving your actions during this particular Interval of Life, it's essential to pause and consider potential consequences before acting. Before making a significant choice today, take a deliberate moment to consider all possible outcomes and how they precisely align with your core values.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Know When To Say No", "description" => "<p>Experimentation during your current Interval of Life often comes with peer pressure. Knowing when to confidently say 'no' helps maintain your well-being and autonomy. If a situation today (or in the future) doesn’t feel right, practice saying 'no' firmly and respectfully.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Stay Connected to Your Core Values", "description" => "<p>With many influences shaping your choices during this particular Interval of Life, staying connected to what truly matters to you prevents you from straying too far from your authentic self. Today, write down your top three core values (e.g., Honesty, authenticity, loyalty) and genuinely reflect on how your actions today precisely align with them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Embrace Both Connecting With Yourself and Social Interaction", "description" => "<p>While connecting with peers is important, connecting with yourself is equally vital for you during this Interval of Life. Spend a minimum of 15 minutes today doing something that helps you deeply reconnect with yourself. Refer to your core stats, locate your first Energy Center, and engage in an activity that specifically 'opens the door' to it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Define Your Personal Boundaries", "description" => "<p>In your current Interval of Life, establishing clear boundaries is crucial for self-preservation and healthy relationships. Today, identify one area where you need to set a clearer boundary and mentally rehearse how you will communicate it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Initiate a Passion Project", "description" => "<p>To truly engage your burgeoning motivations in your current Interval of Life, today, brainstorm and outline the very first steps for a personal project that genuinely excites you, even if it's small.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MOTIVATION", "title" => "Seek Feedback with Purpose", "description" => "<p>In this Interval of Life, constructive feedback is a powerful growth tool. Today, ask a trusted adult or mentor for specific feedback on a recent effort or decision, being open to their insights.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Embrace Exploration with Intention", "description" => "<p>The 'Roadworthy' Interval of Life you are currently experiencing is about purposeful experimentation with new experiences and opportunities. Doing so with intention helps you gain clarity about what aligns with your authentic self. Today, try a new experience (or set a firm intention to do so in the near future), whether it’s a class, a hobby, or meeting new people. Reflect deeply on how it truly aligns with your interests and values. If it does, commit to participating more.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Balance Independence with Reflection", "description" => "<p>Although this period in your life marks physical maturity, true adulthood doesn’t occur for some time. Regularly assessing your choices effectively guides your path. Set aside 10 minutes today to reflect on a recent significant decision and its precise impact on your life journey. Notice if the decision energizes you or causes drain, and set an intention to adjust future choices based on this vital assessment model.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Prioritize Alignment Over Approval", "description" => "<p>It’s tempting to yield to parental or societal expectations during this Interval of Life, but true fulfillment stems from aligning choices with your unique 'vehicle of self,' not just others' opinions. Before making a significant decision today, ask yourself, 'Is this truly what I want and does it align with my unique self, or am I simply attempting to meet someone else’s expectations?'</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Recognize the Value in Diverse Influences", "description" => "<p>Upbringing, culture, and beliefs profoundly shape your perspectives. Embracing positive aspects of these while consciously challenging what doesn’t resonate with you helps define your unique path. Today, identify one core belief or value you hold and deeply consider how it serves your unique journey in this current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Manage Pressure with Perspective", "description" => "<p>The urge to find a career, a partner, or definitive life direction can be intense during this current Interval of Life. Maintaining a broad perspective can prevent overwhelm and confusion. Set a firm intention today that if/when you begin to feel pressure to make a big life choice, you will pause and deliberately remind yourself about the exploratory nature of this current Interval of Life. Before any life-changing choice, consider why you are making it: Is it external pressure, or does the choice genuinely interest, energize, and excite you? If the latter, explore it, as long as it's not harmful.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Celebrate Small Wins", "description" => "<p>Acknowledging progress, even when it seems minor, consistently reinforces confidence. Today, specifically write down one achievement, no matter how small it feels, and take a deliberate moment to genuinely appreciate it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Practice Intention-Based Experimentation", "description" => "<p>This particular Interval of Life you are in is ideal for experimentation, but doing so with clear intention avoids 'throwing spaghetti against the wall.' When trying something new today, set precise intentions for what you hope to gain or learn from the experience.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Build a Foundation for Lifelong Health", "description" => "<p>Choices made now in your current Interval of Life profoundly set the tone for future well-being. Prioritizing health consistently supports sustained energy and overall optimization. Commit to one health-focused action today, like mindfully meal-prepping a nutritious snack or taking a purposeful walk.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Stay Open, Yet Discerned", "description" => "<p>Embracing new experiences is key during your current Interval of Life, but discerning which ones truly resonate with your authentic nature prevents energy drain and misalignment. Today, evaluate one specific activity or commitment in your life and decide if it’s genuinely worth continuing based on its alignment with what truly motivates you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Invest in Understanding Your 'Operating Manual'", "description" => "<p>Understanding how you naturally function fundamentally supports you in making intelligent choices and staying energized as you experience this current Interval of Life you are in. Spend some focused time today reviewing your assessment results videos. Identify and actively commit to three specific activities that you can apply to your day that make you feel most productive and fulfilled.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Network with Purpose", "description" => "<p>During this current Interval of Life, expand your professional or personal network. Today, make a specific effort to connect with one new person in a field or interest area that genuinely intrigues you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Review Your Financial Habits", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are experiencing benefits from establishing financial foundations. Today, review one small aspect of your spending or saving habits. Identify one practical adjustment that aligns with your long-term goals.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Cultivate Mentorship (Both Giving & Receiving)", "description" => "<p>Embrace opportunities to both seek guidance and share your emerging knowledge. Today, reach out to a mentor for advice, or offer a helpful tip to someone who might be newer in a field where you have experience. This strengthens you in your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Document Your Learning Journey", "description" => "<p>To solidify your exploration in this Interval of Life you are in, today, start a simple log or journal documenting new skills you're learning, interesting people you're meeting, and key insights you're gaining.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "ROADWORTHY", "title" => "Set 'Exit Criteria' for Commitments", "description" => "<p>As you experiment in this current Interval of Life, today, establish clear 'exit criteria' for any new commitments (e.g., a new club, a project). This allows you to explore freely, knowing when it's time to move on without guilt if it doesn't serve you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Harness Your Peak Energy Wisely", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life is marked by unmatched physical energy and clarity. Directing that energy into meaningful pursuits ensures you make the absolute most of this powerful phase. Dedicate a focused hour today to a project or goal that genuinely excites you and fully leverages your peak vitality.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Embrace and Celebrate Your Achievements", "description" => "<p>Recognizing your significant progress during your current Life Interval deeply fuels confidence and inspires continued growth. Take a few precise minutes today to write down one recent, impactful achievement and reflect on how it influences your future plans.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Cultivate Balanced Ambition", "description" => "<p>This current Interval of Life you are in is your most powerful and vital, brimming with opportunities. With increased opportunities comes the temptation to overcommit. Balancing ambition with realistic expectations critically prevents burnout. Set a firm intention today that before saying 'yes' to a new commitment, you will pause and rigorously evaluate whether it truly aligns with your unique 'vehicle of self' and whether it genuinely energizes and excites you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Prioritize Meaningful Relationships", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in naturally has significant developments in personal life, such as relationships and family building. Prioritizing these genuine connections strengthens your support network and profoundly enriches your life. Today, reach out to a loved one or close friend and make concrete plans to spend quality, dedicated time together.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Exercise Your 'No' with Confidence", "description" => "<p>Because your current Interval of Life is filled with so much vitality, it can be easy for you to overcommit. Mastering the ability to confidently say 'no' helps maintain laser focus and preserves your energy for your highest priorities. Notice today if an invitation or request doesn’t align with your natural capabilities (it doesn’t give you energy when you consider it), and politely but firmly decline it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Leverage Your Marketability", "description" => "<p>This is the time in your life when your marketability is at its absolute peak. Use it strategically to make impactful career or life moves that effectively set up future success. Today, actively consider how you can optimize your professional profile or take a proactive, tangible step toward a career move that powerfully showcases your current strengths.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Guard Against Overconfidence", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life is your most powerful, which can feel incredibly empowering and even invincible. However, it can also lead to overextension. Staying grounded ensures sustainable growth. Before tackling a major project today, remind yourself to approach it with an openness to learning all you can from the experience, honoring the power of your Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Schedule Regular Self-Check-Ins", "description" => "<p>This particular Interval of Life you are experiencing is the most vital of all, which may have you feeling invincible at times. Periodic self-assessments are crucial to maintain awareness of your limits and recalibrate your priorities effectively. Today, set aside 15 minutes for a precise personal check-in, rigorously evaluating your energy levels and commitments. Set an intention to have these self-check-ins several times a week.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Lay the Foundation for Future Transformations", "description" => "<p>Intelligent decisions made now profoundly pave the way for the next Interval of Life. Proactive planning for the future while optimizing the present strategically sets you up for continued, evolving success. Today, identify one habit or skill that precisely aligns with your 'vehicle of self' that you want to develop to support your future unfoldment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Be a Source of Encouragement", "description" => "<p>Your accumulated experience grants you a unique position to uplift and inspire others, making a significant difference in someone’s day or journey. Today, offer a word of genuine encouragement to someone, authentically reinforcing their strengths or efforts.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Define Your Priorities", "description" => "<p>With your heightened clarity and energy in this current Interval of Life, today, articulate your top 3-5 priorities for the next 6-12 months. This focus leverages your power for maximum impact.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Proactively Seek Stretch Assignments", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life is prime for significant growth. Today, identify one 'stretch' assignment or challenge that will push your capabilities and actively seek opportunities to take it on.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "POWER", "title" => "Map Your Long-Term Vision", "description" => "<p>While in this powerful Interval of Life, today, spend 15-20 minutes outlining a compelling long-term vision (e.g., 5-10 years out) for your life and career. This gives direction to your immense energy.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Embrace Change as Growth", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in is a time where many experiences can feel disruptive. Embracing them as natural and transformative can profoundly shift your perspective. Today, reflect on one recent life event and consciously consider what valuable lesson or opportunity for growth it truly holds.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Stay Present in the Eye of the Storm", "description" => "<p>When life feels overwhelming during this Interval of Life, being deeply present helps reduce anxiety and allows you to respond thoughtfully rather than react impulsively. Practice a 5-minute 'getting present' exercise today: Get comfortable in a seated position, take three deep breaths, focus on an inanimate object (noticing its details), then shift focus to a random body part (e.g., right big toe, belly-button). Repeat this at least three times, choosing new objects and body parts. This exercise helps anchor you in the present moment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Resist Drastic Decisions in Moments of Frustration", "description" => "<p>The urge to 'throw it all away' is common for some experiencing this current Interval of Life you are in. Giving yourself ample space to process prevents regrettable choices. Today, set a firm intention that when you feel an impulse to make a big change, you will take a 24-hour pause to allow your emotions to settle before acting.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Honor the Transformation Process", "description" => "<p>Just like a caterpillar transforming into a butterfly, your journey may involve feeling confined or uncertain at times during your current Interval of Life. Trust that these feelings are a natural part of evolving into a new, more authentic version of yourself. Spend a few moments today journaling about the changes you are noticing about yourself and what positive outcomes you genuinely hope to see.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Avoid Comparing Your Journey to Others’", "description" => "<p>This current Interval of Life you are experiencing can sometimes bring doubts and the illusion that others are ahead of you. Recognizing that everyone’s path is unique fosters genuine contentment. Whether you currently have these doubts or not, reminding yourself of your unique progress is an intelligent action. Today, list three specific accomplishments you’re proud of to powerfully reinforce your unique progress.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Reassess Your Plans & Aspirations", "description" => "<p>Because this current Interval of Life you are in is so transformative, old aspirations can often lose their appeal. Revisiting your aspirations helps align them with your ever-evolving unfoldment. Today, take 10 minutes to reflect on what is most profoundly meaningful to you now. Feel free to journal your thoughts, record a voice memo to yourself, or simply contemplate.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Practice Patience with Yourself", "description" => "<p>This transformational phase of your life can be intense at times. Being gentle and compassionate with yourself as you navigate challenges is crucial for sustaining your energy. Set an intention today that when you feel frustrated, you will take a moment to remind yourself that true transformation is gradual and give yourself grace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Stay Connected to Trusted Sources of Support", "description" => "<p>During this demanding Interval of Life, reaching out to supportive friends, family, or mentors can provide essential stability and reassurance. Reach out to one trusted person today to share your experiences or simply enjoy their supportive company.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Remember: 'This Too Shall Pass'", "description" => "<p>Keeping in mind that this Interval of Life you are experiencing is temporary helps foster profound resilience. Trust that you’ll emerge stronger on the other side. If you are experiencing a challenge today, write down the phrase 'This too shall pass' and place it somewhere visible as a daily reminder of your inherent strength and resilience.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Seek Out Inspiring Narratives of Change", "description" => "<p>To support you based on your current Interval of Life's transformative nature, today, read or listen to a story about someone who successfully navigated significant life changes. Find inspiration in their journey.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Practice Intentional Release", "description" => "<p>Identify one thing you are holding onto (a belief, an old habit, a material item) that no longer serves your evolving self. Today, consciously decide to release it, creating space for your transformation that is naturally unfolding for you during this Interval of Life you are in.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Redefine Success on Your Own Terms", "description" => "<p>In your current Interval of Life, external definitions of success might no longer resonate. Today, spend time clarifying what success truly means to you now, independent of past or societal expectations.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Engage in Expressive Arts", "description" => "<p>Find a creative outlet today (e.g., drawing, painting, writing, playing music) that allows you to express the shifts and emotions you're experiencing in your current Interval of Life without judgment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "MIDLIFE", "title" => "Conduct a 'Life Audit'", "description" => "<p>Today, take 30 minutes to review key areas of your life (career, relationships, health, passions). Identify one area that truly needs realignment for the natural transformation that is occurring for you at this time in your life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],


            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Embrace Your New Perspective", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in is when true adulthood begins, bringing a newfound awareness of life’s impermanence and deeper meaning. Embracing this perspective profoundly fosters gratitude and intentional living. Spend 5 minutes today reflecting on what you’re genuinely grateful for and how this heightened awareness shifts your view of life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Pursue Meaningful Experiences", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life is called the 'Awareness Interval,' and with greater awareness comes an amplified desire for significant, enriching experiences. Prioritizing what truly adds value to your life consistently boosts fulfillment. Plan an activity today that will bring you deep joy or thoughtfully expand your worldview, such as visiting a museum or spending quality, present time with loved ones.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Balance Information Gathering with Action", "description" => "<p>This 'Awareness Interval' of your Life is a vital time to seek knowledge and grow, but it’s essential to apply what you learn rather than getting lost in endless acquisition. Today, implement one new idea or practical piece of knowledge you’ve recently gained directly into your daily routine.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Reinvent Yourself Thoughtfully", "description" => "<p>Having the desire to reinvent yourself during this current Interval of Life is natural and healthy. Staying conscious of not overcommitting to change helps maintain clarity. Today, identify one small, deliberate change you want to make that precisely aligns with your evolving goals and take the very first tangible step.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Prioritize Health and Well-being", "description" => "<p>Recognizing the critical importance of sustaining your body becomes profoundly clearer during this Interval of Life. Maintaining physical health proactively supports ongoing vitality. Dedicate at least 20 minutes today to a physical activity that truly nurtures your well-being.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Avoid the 'Workshop Junkie Syndrome'", "description" => "<p>It’s easy during this current Interval of Life you are in to become engrossed in constant learning without fully integrating new insights. Focus intensely on what truly resonates with you. Today, review one area where you’re investing time (courses, workshops, seminars, instructional videos) and ask yourself if it’s genuinely enriching your life or just adding noise. If it’s just noise, precisely refine your priorities.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Cultivate Presence and Awareness", "description" => "<p>This Interval of your life serves as a powerful reminder that life is short and should be lived fully in the moment. Becoming more aware of each moment helps deepen experiences and significantly reduce stress. Practice a 5-minute exercise today to enhance your connection to the present: Get comfortable in a seated position, take three deep breaths, focus on an inanimate object (noticing its details), then shift focus to a random body part (e.g., right big toe, belly-button). Repeat this at least three times, choosing new objects and body parts.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Deepen Your Relationships", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life comes with an increased awareness of life’s finite nature. Because of this, nurturing relationships takes on new, profound meaning. Building strong, authentic connections adds immense richness to life. Today, reach out to a friend or family member and engage in a heartfelt, meaningful conversation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Practice Self-Compassion", "description" => "<p>Your particular Interval of Life can involve reinvention and embracing new awareness, which may come with challenges. Being gentle with yourself fosters resilience and deep personal growth. If you feel frustrated or unsure today (or any day), gently remind yourself that growth is a continuous process, and it’s perfectly okay to take things one step at a time.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Set Intentions for Future Growth", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are experiencing serves as a profound transition to a more mature phase of life. Setting clear intentions ensures that your next steps are meaningful and precisely aligned with your deeper awareness. Today, write down one specific intention for the week that supports your personal growth, whether it’s related to your career, hobbies, or health.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Engage in Reflective Writing", "description" => "<p>To process your newfound awareness in this Interval of Life, today, dedicate 15 minutes to reflective writing about a significant life event or personal insight.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Seek 'Aha!' Moments", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life is ripe for breakthroughs. Today, actively seek out something that sparks an 'aha!' moment, whether through reading, conversation, or quiet contemplation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Practice Mindful Consumption", "description" => "<p>In this Interval of Life, consciously choose to consume information, food, or experiences mindfully. Today, practice savoring one meal or truly focusing on one experience you are having without distraction.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Reconnect with Past Passions", "description" => "<p>Think back to a passion or hobby from your younger years that you've set aside. Today, revisit it, even for a few minutes. Your current Interval of Life's awareness may bring new insights.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "AWARENESS", "title" => "Define Your Legacy (Early Thoughts)", "description" => "<p>While still in the 'Awareness Interval,' today, spend a few minutes contemplating what kind of impact or legacy you'd ideally like to leave. This type of thinking aligns with your Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Share Your Wisdom Generously", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in is a time when accumulated knowledge and experiences become invaluable gifts you can share. Mentorship and guiding others profoundly enriches both you and those around you. Today, identify one specific skill or hard-earned lesson you can share, whether through conversation, formal mentoring, or writing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Engage in Meaningful Community Activities", "description" => "<p>Contributing to causes that genuinely resonate with your natural talents and cultivated expertise not only benefits others but reinforces your own sense of purpose in your current Interval of Life. Today, make a concrete commitment to volunteer for a future activity that aligns with your interests and skills.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Reflect on Your Journey with Gratitude", "description" => "<p>Acknowledging your life's unique path deeply fosters gratitude and a profound understanding of your resilience and achievements. Spend 10 minutes today reflecting on key moments of your life that have truly shaped you and contributed to your current purpose as you experience this Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Maintain Physical Health for Longevity", "description" => "<p>With a lifetime of experience comes the crucial responsibility of maintaining your body for the years ahead. Incorporate 30 minutes of intentional exercise today, whether it's walking, yoga, or any activity you genuinely enjoy. This supports the importance of remaining vital in this current Interval of Life and beyond.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Embrace Personal Forgiveness", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in often brings profound opportunities for personal forgiveness, letting go of past regrets or conflicts. Embracing this releases significant mental burdens. Today, spend a few minutes reflecting on one specific situation or relationship where you can offer forgiveness to yourself and others. Remain objective in your desire to simply forgive – letting go of any desire to rehash, blame, or hold onto regrets. Speak it aloud or write it down that you forgive yourself for your part and the other person for theirs.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Celebrate Your Unique Path", "description" => "<p>This particular Interval of Life you are in has you growing comfortable in your own skin. You can actively support this unfolding comfort by recognizing the profound worth in your journey – it adds both confidence and peace. Today, acknowledge three specific qualities that you genuinely love about yourself and how they have served you well. Write down these qualities and post them where you can see them every day.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Cultivate Deeper Connections", "description" => "<p>The Interval of Life you are currently experiencing naturally shifts focus towards relationships that are truly fulfilling and mutually enriching, rather than those that are obligatory and draining. Spending time nurturing these enriching connections enhances your sense of community and support. Today, reach out to one of those connections, whether a close friend or family member, for a conversation that deeply strengthens your bond.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Balance Altruism with Self-Care", "description" => "<p>While giving back is a central theme of your current Interval of Life, preserving your energy through deliberate self-care is crucial for sustainability. Today, dedicate an hour to a self-care activity that genuinely rejuvenates you. Seek out a lifestyle activity that specifically engages your first (or primary) Energy Center.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Embrace Your Purpose", "description" => "<p>Recognizing that your purpose is larger than individual achievements brings profound fulfillment. Engage with activities that remind you of the unique gifts you offer in the world. Today, spend 20 minutes contemplating how your work or contributions impact others and the legacy you truly wish to leave behind. Journal or record your insights.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Be a Source of Encouragement", "description" => "<p>During this current Interval of Life you are experiencing, your accumulated experience grants you a unique position to uplift and inspire others, making a significant difference in someone’s day or journey. Today, offer a word of genuine encouragement to someone, authentically reinforcing their strengths or efforts.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Mentor Someone Informally", "description" => "<p>Today, offer a piece of unsolicited, helpful advice or share a relevant experience with someone younger or less experienced in your field. This directly engages your Interval of Life's 'Pay It Forward' nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Document a Life Lesson", "description" => "<p>Today, choose one life lesson you've learned and briefly write it down. This act of documenting your wisdom aligns with your Interval of Life's purpose of sharing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Offer Practical Assistance", "description" => "<p>Your accumulated skills are valuable. Today, offer practical assistance to someone who needs it – perhaps helping with a task, sharing expertise, or offering a ride. This embodies your Interval of Life's contribution.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "PAYIT", "title" => "Create a 'Gratitude Legacy' List", "description" => "<p>Today, start a list of all the people who have positively impacted your life. This act of gratitude reinforces your Interval of Life's focus on connection and appreciation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Embrace Your Newfound Freedom", "description" => "<p>This stage of your life is about releasing old burdens and enjoying life more fully. Embracing this freedom fosters deep joy and true relaxation. Take 15 minutes today to reflect on one specific responsibility you’ve recently let go of and consciously appreciate the space it has created for you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Explore Activities That Spark Joy", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life you are in for most people naturally has fewer responsibilities, making it the perfect time to engage in hobbies and activities that bring pure happiness and genuine fulfillment. Activate a new or cherished old favorite activity today, such as dancing, painting, or gardening.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Respect Your Bandwidth", "description" => "<p>While this Interval of Life offers the chance to do more, understanding and rigorously respecting your physical and mental limits is key to sustainable enjoyment. Plan your day today with a conscious balance of activity and restorative rest, ensuring you never overextend yourself.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Continue Lifelong Learning", "description" => "<p>Curiosity doesn’t end with age; it thrives! This Interval of Life you are in benefits immensely from exploring new topics, as it keeps your mind sharp and enriches your life experience. Dedicate 30 minutes today to reading about or researching something you’re genuinely curious about, whether it's history, a new language, or emerging technology.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Prioritize Social Connections", "description" => "<p>Your current Interval of Life benefits significantly from engaging with friends, family, or community groups, as it enhances joy and effectively combats isolation. Today, schedule a call or meeting with a friend, or proactively join a group activity that genuinely interests you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Maintain Physical Activity", "description" => "<p>Regular, gentle physical activity consistently supports energy levels and overall well-being, allowing you to fully enjoy this liberating Interval of Life. Commit to 20 minutes of light, enjoyable exercise today, such as a walk, a swim, gentle stretching, or restorative yoga.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Celebrate Small Wins and Simple Pleasures", "description" => "<p>Life’s simplicity can be its greatest gift in this stage of your life. Finding profound joy in small, everyday moments greatly enhances your quality of life. Today, identify one simple pleasure—savoring a good meal, enjoying a sunrise, listening to a favorite song—and take dedicated time to fully appreciate it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Pursue New Passions", "description" => "<p>This Interval of Life for so many invites active exploration of new interests without the past constraints of career or heavy responsibility. Today, consider exploring a class or workshop related to a new hobby you might like to experience, such as photography, cooking, or music.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Practice Gratitude for Your Journey", "description" => "<p>Recognizing your life’s path and the diverse experiences that brought you here can deepen your sense of fulfillment and peace throughout this Interval of Life you are experiencing. Today, write down three specific things you are genuinely grateful for that relate to your past achievements or life experiences.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Reflect on Your Legacy", "description" => "<p>Thinking about the specific mark you wish to leave can offer a profound sense of purpose and effectively guide your actions during this phase of your life. Spend a few moments today reflecting on how you want to be remembered and what concrete actions today align with that vision.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Reconnect with a Beloved Pastime", "description" => "<p>Think of an activity you once loved but set aside due to other demands. Today, dedicate time to reconnecting with that pastime, allowing you to connect with the freedom that exists for you in your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Enjoy a 'Digital Detox' Moment", "description" => "<p>To fully embrace the liberation that exists for you in this Interval of Life you are in, today, choose a specific time to completely unplug from all digital devices for at least an hour. Notice the peace and presence it brings to your Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Plan a 'Joy List' for the Week", "description" => "<p>Today, create a simple list of 3-5 activities that genuinely bring you joy and that you want to experience this week. Make intentional plans to incorporate them into your schedule. This exercise will activate the liberated nature of your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "LIBERATED", "title" => "Explore a New Genre", "description" => "<p>Expand your horizons in your current Interval of Life. Today, try reading a book, watching a film, or listening to music in a genre you wouldn't typically choose.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Embrace the Power of Letting Go", "description" => "<p>This period of your life often involves the natural release of less important memories and responsibilities. Letting go of non-essential burdens profoundly helps maintain mental clarity and inner peace. Today, identify one specific thought, worry, or task that you can consciously choose to release to create valuable mental space.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Use Lists to Support Memory", "description" => "<p>Writing notes and maintaining simple lists can effectively help compensate for natural changes in memory and significantly reduce stress during your current Interval of Life. Today, create a concise list of tasks or reminders for the day to keep yourself organized and at ease.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Share Your Wisdom with Others", "description" => "<p>Your rich life experiences are immensely valuable to younger generations. Sharing stories and insights fosters deep connection and a profound sense of purpose. Today, reach out to a family member or friend and share a specific life lesson or a meaningful story with them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Accept Physical Changes with Grace", "description" => "<p>Within your current Interval of Life, physical changes are an inevitable and natural part of the journey. Embracing these changes with grace can enhance acceptance and deep self-compassion. Today, acknowledge one specific aspect of your body with profound gratitude, recognizing its resilience and what it has carried you through over the years.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Prioritize Gentle Self-Care", "description" => "<p>Consistent self-care profoundly supports your well-being and helps you stay energized. Consistent, moderate routines are key. Dedicate 15 minutes today to a soothing activity like light stretching, taking a warm bath, or practicing gentle breathing exercises, nurturing yourself through your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Nurture a Healthy Diet", "description" => "<p>Eating well is fundamental for maintaining energy and supporting overall health. Today, consciously prepare or enjoy a nutritious meal that includes a balanced mix of vegetables, lean proteins, and healthy fats.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Foster Restful Sleep", "description" => "<p>Adequate rest is crucial for mental and physical health, particularly as the body undergoes the natural changes that occur during this Interval of Life. Create a calming bedtime routine tonight, such as reading something inspirational, listening to calming music, or doing light breathing exercises.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Practice Reflection and Gratitude", "description" => "<p>Reflecting on your life’s journey during your current Interval of Life and authentically expressing gratitude can bring deeper fulfillment and profound contentment. Spend 5 minutes today journaling about one cherished memory or something specific you are deeply grateful for.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Engage in Light Exercise", "description" => "<p>Regular, gentle exercise supports mobility and well-being, significantly enhancing your quality of life. Take a short, deliberate walk today or practice a few simple movements to maintain flexibility and circulation.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Embrace Simplicity", "description" => "<p>Simplifying activities and tasks prevents feeling overwhelmed and consistently promotes peace of mind. Streamline one part of your daily routine today, such as setting a gentle timer to remind you to get up and move, hydrate, or enjoy a healthy snack.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Listen to Calming Audio", "description" => "<p>To promote inner peace in your current Interval of Life, today, listen to a calming audiobook, a guided meditation, or gentle instrumental music that truly resonates with you.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Review Cherished Photos", "description" => "<p>Today, spend some time looking through old photo albums or digital pictures that evoke fond memories and a sense of gratitude for your life's journey.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Practice Mindful Eating", "description" => "<p>When you have a meal or snack today, eat slowly and mindfully, savoring each bite. This brings you fully into the present moment of your Interval of Being.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "BEING", "title" => "Write a Letter of Appreciation", "description" => "<p>Today, write a short letter or email to someone who has positively impacted your life, expressing your gratitude. This act of appreciation enhances your Interval of Being.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],

            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Embrace Life Review with Openness", "description" => "<p>This stage of your life actively invites natural reflection on past experiences. Embracing this process helps make profound peace with both joys and regrets. Set aside 15 minutes today to thoughtfully think back on a significant life event and deeply reflect on what you learned from it.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Practice Forgiveness and Letting Go", "description" => "<p>The capacity to truly forgive and let go of past grievances fosters emotional freedom and deep contentment. Spend a few minutes today reflecting on one specific situation or relationship where you can genuinely offer forgiveness to yourself and others. Remain objective in your desire to simply forgive – letting go of any desire to rehash, blame, or hold onto regrets. Speak it out loud or write it down that you forgive yourself for your part and the other person for their part. This is vital as you support yourself in your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Accept Physical Changes Gracefully", "description" => "<p>Within your current Interval of Life, physical changes are inevitable and natural. Acceptance enhances self-compassion and reduces unnecessary stress. Today, take a moment to genuinely appreciate what your body has carried you through, even with its changes and any limitations you may be experiencing.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Engage Consciously with the Present", "description" => "<p>Being deeply present in each moment cultivates a profound sense of peace and enjoyment. Practice a brief exercise today (and every day), focusing on your senses and surroundings to stay anchored in the present: Get comfortable in a seated position, take three deep breaths, focus on an inanimate object (noticing its details), then shift focus to a random body part (e.g., right big toe, belly-button, or left shoulder). Repeat this exercise at least three times. This spatial awareness exercise helps you reference yourself in the present moment.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Cultivate Simplicity in Daily Life", "description" => "<p>Simplifying activities and routines during this Interval of Life brings clarity and significantly reduces mental clutter. Today, choose one daily task to simplify by setting a timer for yourself to take appropriate breaks or by breaking down the task into smaller, manageable parts that can be completed over a few days.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Share Your Stories and Wisdom", "description" => "<p>Sharing rich life experiences with younger generations during this Interval of Life offers invaluable insights and profoundly strengthens bonds. Today, reach out to a family member or friend to share a significant story or a wisdom-filled lesson from your past that could truly inspire or guide them.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Embrace Surrender and Peace", "description" => "<p>This Life Interval you are in often brings a powerful sense of surrender – an acceptance of what is genuinely beyond your control. Embracing this can lead to a profound sense of peace. Today, reflect on one specific aspect of your life that you have been trying to control and practice consciously releasing it mentally.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Prioritize Meaningful Engagements", "description" => "<p>Consciously choosing how to spend your time and whom to share it with makes interactions more fulfilling. Plan to connect with someone today who genuinely brings joy and meaning to your life, even if it’s just a phone call. This honors the nature of your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Celebrate Your Journey", "description" => "<p>Acknowledging your life’s path, encompassing both hardships and triumphs, deeply fosters gratitude and powerful self-recognition. Today, write down or share aloud three specific triumphs or moments you are genuinely proud of.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Foster a Sense of Wonder", "description" => "<p>This stage of your life continues to offer boundless opportunities for awe and curiosity, which keep your spirit youthful and engaged. Spend time today exploring something that truly piques your curiosity, whether it’s reading, watching a documentary, or simply observing nature.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Create a 'Gratitude Chronicle'", "description" => "<p>Today, dedicate time to writing down specific people, places, or events from your past for which you are deeply grateful. This act reinforces the positive aspects of your life review.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Listen to Calming Music or Sounds", "description" => "<p>To support inner tranquility in your current Interval of Life, today, listen to music or nature sounds that bring you a sense of calm and peace.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Review Cherished Mementos", "description" => "<p>Today, spend a few minutes looking at cherished photographs or objects that hold significant memories for you, allowing those positive feelings to surface.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Practice Mindful Appreciation", "description" => "<p>Today, choose one simple daily activity (like having a cup of tea or looking out a window) and engage with it fully, mindfully appreciating the sensory experience. This anchors you in your current Interval of Life.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],
            ["code" => "REVIEW", "title" => "Connect with Loved Ones Remotely", "description" => "<p>If in-person visits aren't always possible, today, make a conscious effort to connect with a loved one through a video call or a heartfelt phone conversation, maintaining those vital bonds.</p>", "created_at" => now(), "updated_at" => now()],




        ];
